var book = {
	"name": "UMSEBENZI WABATHUNYWA",
	"numChapters": 28,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kwincwadi yam yokuqala, Tiyofilo, ndabhala ndibalisa ngazo zonke izinto uYesu awasungula ngazo ukwenza nokufundisa,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> kude kuye kuthi gaa ngaloo mhla wanyuselwa ngawo ezulwini nguThixo. Ngaphambi kokuba anyuswe uYesu, wathi ngoMoya oyiNgcwele wawayala loo madoda awawanyulayo ukuba abe *ngabathunywa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Emva kokubandezelwa nokufa kwakhe wazibonakalisa kuloo madoda ngeziganeko ezininzi ukuba uvukile. Kwithuba leentsuku ezingamashumi amane abathunywa babemana bembona, ethetha nabo ebaxelela ngezolawulo lukaThixo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Esitya kunye nabo wabayala wathi: “Ze ningemki eJerusalem. Hlalani nilinde isipho esathenjiswa nguBawo, esiya ndanixelela ngaso.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kaloku uYohane yena wayebabhaptiza ngamanzi abantu; ke nina, kungekudala, uThixo uza kunibhaptiza ngoMoya oyiNgcwele.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Xa babendawonye, abathunywa bambuza uYesu besithi: “Nkosi, ngaba uza kulubuyisela kwangoku na ulawulo kumaSirayeli?”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> UYesu uphendule wathi: “Asiyondawo yenu ukuwazi amathuba namaxesha uBawo agqiba yedwa ngawo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nina niya kunikwa amandla, akufika kuni uMoya oyiNgcwele, nindingqinele ebantwini baseJerusalem, nabakulo lonke elakwaJuda, nabaseSamariya, kude kuse naseziphelweni zomhlaba.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Akuba etshilo uYesu, wanyuselwa ezulwini, bejongile abafundi bakhe. Lamsitha ilifu, ababa sambona.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Besakhangele ukumka kwakhe, bondele esibhakabhakeni apho, nango amadoda amabini, ambethe ezimhlophe, emi ngakubo,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> abuza athi: “Madoda, maGalili, nimele ntoni apha nikhangele phezulu nje? UYesu lo nimbone enyuselwa ezulwini, uya kubuya kwangolu hlobo nimbone esimka ngalo.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Baza babuyela eJerusalem, bevela entabeni ekuthiwa yeyeMinquma, ekufuphi neJerusalem umgama omalunga nekhilomitha enye.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bakungena esixekweni, banyukela egumbini eliphezulu, apho babehlala khona. YayinguPetros, noYohane, noYakobi, noAndreya; uFilipu noTomas; uBhartolomeyu noMatewu; uYakobi unyana ka-Alifeyu, noSimon iTsha-ntliziyo, kwakunye noJudas unyana kaYakobi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bonke aba babezingisa ukuthandaza ngamxhelo mnye, kukho namanina, ekho noMariya unina kaYesu nabantakwabo-Yesu.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngaloo mihla xa babehlangene ndawonye abakholwayo bemalunga nekhulu elinamashumi amabini bebonke, waphakama uPetros, wathi:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Madoda, mawethu, bekufanelekile ukuba kuzaliseke okwathethwa nguMoya oyiNgcwele, esebenzisa uDavide ukuxela okuya kwenzeka kuJudas, lowo wabakhokelela kuYesu abo bambambayo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> UJudas lo ebengomnye wethu, enenxaxheba kulo msebenzi sikuwo.” (",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kaloku le ndoda yathenga umhlaba ngaloo mali yayifumana ngenkohlakalo. Yawa ngesisu, sagqabhuka, zaphalala izibilini kuloo ndawo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Le ntlekele yaduma kulo lonke elaseJerusalem; baza bayithiya igama loo ndawo, bathi yiAkeldama ngolwini lwabo, igama elithetha umhlaba wegazi.)",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Kuba kaloku kwiNcwadi yeeNdumiso kubhalwe kwathiwa: “ ‘Mawube linxiwa umzi wakhe; makungahlali nabani kuwo.’ “Kwakhona kuthiwa: “ ‘Masithathwe ngomnye isikhundla sakhe.’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Ngoko ke, makubekho enye indoda ethatha indawo yakhe. Kufuneka ibe ngumntu obesoloko ekunye nathi ngalo lonke elaa xesha iNkosi yayijikeleza phakathi kwethu; umntu owayekho ukususela kanye ngelaa xesha uYohane wayebhaptiza, kude kuze kuthi gaa ngomhla wonyuko. Nguloo mntu ke onokungqina kunye nathi ngokuvuka kweNkosi yethu.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Baza baphakamisa amagama amadoda amabini: uJosefu owayesaziwa ngokuba nguBharsabha, obizwa nangokuba nguYusto, kwakunye noMatiya.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bathandaza ke benjenje: “Nkosi, wena uzaziyo iingcinga zeentliziyo zabantu bonke, sahlulele phakathi kwala madoda mabini, usibonise eyona uyinyulele",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> kwisikhundla sokukukhonza *ingumthunywa, eso satyeshelwa nguJudas ukuze aye kuloo ndawo imfaneleyo.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Abhalwa ke la magama omabini, kwenziwa *amaqashiso, kwaphumelela elikaMatiya; waza wabalelwa ekubeni ngumthunywa kunye nabanye abalishumi elinanye."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ekufikeni komhla *wePentekoste babehlangene ndawonye bonke.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ngesaquphe beva isandi esingathi kukuza komoya omkhulu, uvuthuza esibhakabhakeni. Sayizalisa indlu ababehleli kuyo isandi eso.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kwabonakala amadangatye angathi ziilwimi, laza lalelo idangatye lahlala kumntu ngamnye kubo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bazaliswa ke bonke nguMoya oyiNgcwele, baza bathetha ngalwimi zimbi, njengoko uMoya wabaphayo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> EJerusalem apho kwakukho amaJuda, abantu ababenenzondelelo ngezinto zikaThixo, bevela kuzo zonke izizwe zehlabathi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bakukuva oko kwakusenzeka, kwahlanganisana indimbane yabantu, bonke bemangalisiwe kukuva abalandeli bakaYesu bethetha iilwimi zabo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bethe khumnqa, bathi: “Okunene aba bantu ngamaGalili bonke!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ke, kutheni le nto sonke ngabanye sibeva bethetha nathi ngolwimi lweenkobe?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Thina singamaParti, namaMedi, namaElam, nabaseMesopotami, nabakwaJuda, nabaseKapadoki; singabasePonto naseAsiya,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> eFrigi nasePamfili, naseJiputa nabemimandla yaseLibhiya engaseKirene, nabahambi abavela eRoma.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> SingamaJuda nabangeni buJudeni, amaKrete nama-Arabhu. Siyabeva beyithetha ngeelwimi zethu imisebenzi yamandla kaThixo.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bethe nqa ke bexakiwe, babuzana bathi: “Awu! Ngaba ithetha ntoni le nto?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Abanye baphoxisa ngabo, bathi: “À, suka! Banxilile!”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Waphakama uPetros, wabhekisa ebantwini, ethetha egameni labafundi abalishumi elinambini, wathi: “Mawethu, maJuda, nani nonke bemi baseJerusalem, phulaphulani nibeke iindlebe, nantsi indawo emaniyiqonde:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> La madoda akanxilanga njengoko niba kunjalo nina, kuba kusekusasa ngentlazane,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> koko le nto yenzekayo yileya yaxelwa *ngumshumayeli uJoweli esithi:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “ ‘Yiyo le into endiya kuyenza ngemihla yokugqibela;’ utsho uThixo: ‘Ndiya kugalela uMoya wam kulo lonke uluntu, oonyana neentombi zenu zishumayele, abafana babone imibono, amaxhego aphuphe amaphupha.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ewe, nezicaka nezicakazana zam ndiya kuzigalela ngoMoya wam ngaloo mihla, zize zishumayele.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ndiya kwenza imiqondiso esibhakabhakeni phezulu, nezimanga emhlabeni phantsi. Kuya kubakho igazi nomlilo nentshinyela yomsi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ilanga liya kujika libe bubumnyama, inyanga ibe bomvu njengegazi, phambi kokufika kwaloo mhla mkhulu udumileyo weNkosi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kananjalo nabani na othe wabiza igama leNkosi uya kusindiswa.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “MaSirayeli, phulaphulani la mazwi: UYesu waseNazarete yindoda eyâlathwa nguThixo, yaza yabonakaliswa ngemisebenzi yamandla nemimangaliso nangemiqondiso awayenzayo uThixo ngayo. Nani ngokwenu niyayazi loo nto, kuba yenzeka phakathi kwenu apha.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Lo Yesu ke, wanikelwa kuni ngokuthanda nangokwazi kukaThixo, nambulala ngokumnikela ukuba abethelelwe emnqamlezweni ngabantu abangawukhathalelanga umthetho wethu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> UThixo ke yena wamvusa, wamkhulula kwiintlungu zokufa, kuba ukufa kwakungenawo amandla okumbophelela.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kaloku uDavide uthi ngaye: “ ‘Ndasoloko ndiyibona iNkosi iphambi kwam ngamaxesha onke. Yintonga yam yasekhosi iNkosi, ngoko andiyi kuchukunyiswa nto.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kungoko yagcobayo intliziyo yam, ndathetha ndinemivuyo. Ngaphezu koko ndiya kuhlala ndinethemba lokuba andiyi kufa,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> kuba akuyi kuwuyeka kwelabafileyo umphefumlo wam, ungayi kusiyeka sibole isicaka sakho esikholekileyo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Undazisile iindlela zobomi; ndaye ndiya kuzala luvuyo ngenxa yobukho bakho.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Mawethu, mandithethe ngokucacileyo kuni ngokhokho wethu uDavide. Yena wafa, waza wangcwatywa; yaye nengcwaba lakhe lilapha unanamhlanje.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Njengokuba *wayengumshumayeli, wayesazi isithembiso sokuba uThixo wafunga ukuba omnye kubazukulwana bakhe uya kuba ngukumkani njengaye.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Walubona ke kwangaphambili uvuko lukaKrestu, wathetha ngalo, exela ukuba akayi kuyekwa kwelabafileyo, futhi engayi kubola.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> UThixo ke wamvusa ekufeni lo Yesu; saye ke thina sonke singamangqina aloo nto.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Njengoko anyuselwe ewongeni kuThixo, wamkele uMoya oyiNgcwele, lowo wathenjiswayo nguYise. Le nto ke niyibonayo niyivayo ngoku kukugalelwa kwaloo Moya kuthi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kaloku uDavide akanyukelanga ezulwini yena ngokwakhe, koko uthi: “ ‘INkosi yathi eNkosini yam: Hlala ngakum kweli wonga",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> lo gama ndikoyisela iintshaba zakho.’",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Ngenxa yoko qinisekani, mzi kaSirayeli, ukuba lo Yesu enambethelela emnqamlezweni, uThixo ummisele wayiNkosi *ekwanguKrestu.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Yabahlabanisela kakhulu intetho kaPetros abantu, bakuba beyivile; baza bathi kuPetros *nabathunywa ababenaye: “Kufuneka senze ntoni, mawethu?”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Wathi uPetros kubo: “Guqukani ezonweni zenu nonke ngabanye, nibhaptizwe egameni likaYesu Krestu, ukuze nixolelwe izono zenu, nize namkele isipho soMoya oyiNgcwele.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Kuba isithembiso esenziwa nguThixo senzelwa nina nabantwana benu, kwanâbo bakude, bebonke abo iNkosi uThixo wethu ibabizayo.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Wathetha wophela ke uPetros ebaluleka esithi: “Zahlukaniseni naba bantu bakhohlakeleyo, khon' ukuze ningehlelwa sisohlwayo sabo.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Abantu abaninzi balwamkela olu daba, baza babhaptizwa. Baba ngamawaka amathathu abantu abongezelelwayo enanini labo.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Babehlangana rhoqo, bedlelana ngokuphulaphula iimfundiso zabathunywa, nangokuqhekeza isonka, nangokuthandaza.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Imiqondiso nemimangaliso emininzi awayenza *ngabathunywa uThixo yatsho yabakhohla abantu.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Bonke abakholwayo bahlala bebambene, bedlelana ngezinto abanazo omnye nomnye.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Babethengisa ngempahla yabo, babelane ngemali leyo ngokweentswelo zomntu ngamnye.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Imihla ngemihla babehlangana rhoqo *endlwini kaThixo, babuye batye kunye emakhaya bechwayitile bebelezelana,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> bembonga uThixo, bamkelekile kubantu bonke. Mihla le uThixo wayelongeza inani labo ngabo basindiswayo."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngamhla uthile uPetros noYohane baya *endlwini kaThixo ngexesha lomthandazo, ngentsimbi yesithathu emva kwemini.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Apho esangweni lendlu kaThixo ekwakusithiwa liSango eLihle, kwakukho indoda eyayisisiqhwala kwasekuzalweni kwayo. Yayidla ngokusiwa khona yonke imihla ukuze icele amalizo kwabangenayo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Yakubona uPetros noYohane bengena, yacela ukuba bayilize.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bayijonga, waza uPetros wathi: “Khangela apha!”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Yajonga kubo ke ilindele into abaza kuyinika yona.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Uthe uPetros: “Imali andinayo, kodwa ndiza kukunika into endinayo – egameni likaYesu Krestu waseNazarete, ndithi kuwe: ‘Phakama, uhambe.’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Akuba etshilo, wayibamba ngesandla sokunene, wayiphakamisa. Ngoko nangoko iinyawo namaqatha ayo omelela.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Yatsho umtsi, yema ngeenyawo, yahamba-hamba. Yaza yangena nabo endlwini kaThixo, ihamba itsiba-tsiba, ibulela uThixo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bonke abantu ababelapho bayibona ihamba ibulela uThixo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Baqonda ukuba ngulaa mngqibi wayedla ngokuhlala eSangweni eLihle lendlu kaThixo, bonke bathi manga yinto eyenzeke kuye.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Njengoko le ndoda yathi nca kuPetros noYohane, basuka abantu beza begxalathelana kubo bemangalisiwe evarandeni ekuthiwa yekaSolomon.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Akubabona abantu, uPetros wabhekisa kubo wathi: “MaSirayeli, kungani ukuba inimangalise le nto? Khona kutheni ukuba nisijonge ngathi wenziwe ngamandla ethu nangokwethu ukukholeka kuThixo ukuba ahambe lo mntu?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> UThixo ka-Abraham, kaIsake, kaYakobi, uThixo woobawo bethu, ngesi senzo usinike iwonga isicaka sakhe uYesu. Nina namnikela namkhanyela phambi koPilato, nangona yena wayefuna ukumkhulula.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namkhanyela umnyulwa olilungisa! Endaweni yakhe nacela uPilato ukuba anikhululele isihange.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nayibulala imbangi yobomi; ke yena uThixo wayivusa ekufeni. Yeyona nto singqina yona ke leyo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kukuvuma nokuzinikela kwigama likaYesu okuyomelezileyo le ndoda niyibonayo, niyaziyo. Ligunya legama lakhe elimenze waphila njengokuba nimbona elapha phambi kwenu nje lo mntu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Ndiyazi ke, mawethu, ukuba nina neenkokheli zenu le nto niyenze kuYesu ngokungazi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Loo nto ngoko uThixo wayazisayo ngabo bonke *abashumayeli, yokuba umelwe kukubandezeleka, uyizalisekisile.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Guqukani ke ngoko, nibuyele kuThixo, ukuze zicinywe izono zenu;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> nize nifumane amathuba okuhlaziyeka komoya evela eNkosini, nokuze imthumele uYesu onguKrestu oselenikwe nina.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Yena uya kuhlala ezulwini kude kufike ixesha lokuhlaziywa kwezinto zonke, njengoko uThixo wâzisáyo mandulo ngabashumayeli bakhe abanyuliweyo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kaloku uMosis wathi: ‘INkosi uThixo wenu iya kunithumela umshumayeli ophuma kwalapha kumawenu njengam. Maze nimphulaphule kuyo yonke into anixelela yona.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Nabani na ke ongamphulaphuliyo lo mshumayeli uya kusikwa ebantwini bakaThixo atshatyalaliswe.’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Abashumayeli bonke ukususela kuSamweli nabo bamlandeláyo, bayixela le mihla sikuyo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nisisizukulwana sabashumayeli, ninenxaxheba kumnqophiso owenziwa nguThixo nooyihlo-mkhulu, xa wathi kuAbraham: ‘Ngesinqe sakho ndiya kubasikelela bonke abantu bomhlaba.’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> UThixo ke esimisele isiCaka sakhe wasithumela kuni kuqala, ukuze anenzele inceba niguquke kwinkohlakalo yenu.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kwathi uPetros noYohane besathetha nabo abantu, kwafika ababingeleli nentloko yabalindi *bendlu kaThixo kunye *nabaSadusi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Babekhathazekile kuba aba *bathunywa babefundisa abantu ngokuvuka kukaYesu ekufeni, nto leyo yayiqinisekisa ukuba abafileyo baya kuvuka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bababamba ke, babafaka entolongweni, ukuba balinde khona kude kube ngengomso, njengoko imini yayiselisangene.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Uninzi lwâbo bayivayo imfundiso leyo lwakholwa, laza ke landa inani labo laya kumawaka amahlanu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngomhla olandelayo iinkokheli zamaJuda, nabadala, nabachazi-mthetho, bahlangana eJerusalem.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> YayingooAnas umbingeleli omkhulu, noKayafa, noYohane, noAlesandire, kwanabanye bendlu yombingeleli omkhulu, ababelapho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Babamisa phambi kwabo abathunywa, bababuza bathi: “Niyenze kanjani le nto? Gunya lini eli ninalo? Ligama likabani eli nisebenze ngalo?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UPetros, ezele nguMoya oyiNgcwele, wabaphendula wathi: “Ziphathamandla nani badala,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> xa namhlanje nisixoxisa ngesenzo esihle sokuphiliswa komntu osisiqhwala,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> nina ninamaSirayeli ewonke yazini le nto ke: Lo mntu umi apha phambi kwenu ephile qete, uphile ngenxa yegunya legama likaYesu Krestu waseNazarete. Lowo nina nambethelela emnqamlezweni; wamvusa ke yena uThixo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Lo Yesu ngulowo zithi *iziBhalo xa zithetha ngaye: “ ‘Ilitye enalidelayo nina bakhi laba lelona litye lesiseko.’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Usindiso lufumaneka ngaye kuphela, kuba akukho wumbi emhlabeni ogama uThixo alinike uluntu, esingasindiswa ngalo.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Amalungu *eBhunga amangaliswa kukubona ukungafihlisi kukaPetros noYohane, eqonda ukuba bangabantu nje abaqhelekileyo abangenamfundo. Baphawula nokuba babengamahlakani kaYesu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kodwa babengenandlela yokuphikisana nabo, kuba indoda le yayiphilisiwe yayimi apho kunye noPetros noYohane.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Babakhuphela ngaphandle kwendlu leyo yeBhunga, basala bona bexoxa bodwa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Babuzana besithi: “Singawathini la madoda? Wonke ubani apha eJerusalem uyazi ukuba lo mqondiso ungaqhelekanga wenziwe ngawo, sibe ke thina singenako ukuyiphika le nto.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ukuze ke inganwenwi le nto phakathi kwabantu, masibalumkise bangaze bathethe nakubani ngegama likaYesu.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Babangenisa kwakhona, baza babayala ukuba ze bangaphindi bathethe okanye bafundise ngegama likaYesu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> UPetros noYohane bona baphendula bathi: “Zahluleleni nina ngokwenu ukuba kulunge kuphi na phambi koThixo; kukho ukwenza intando yenu, kukho nokwenza intando kaThixo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Thina asinakuyeka ukuthetha ngento esiyibone sayiva ngokwethu.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> IBhunga labatyityimbisela umnwe, laza labakhulula. Alibanga nakroba lakubohlwaya, ngenxa yokoyika abantu, kuba babedumisa uThixo ngesi senzo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kaloku le ndoda yaphiliswa ngalo mmangaliso yayingaphezu kwamashumi amane eminyaka ubudala.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bakuba bekhululwe uPetros noYohane babuyela kubahlobo babo, bababalisela okwathethwa kubo ngababingeleli abaziintloko bekunye nabadala.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bevile ke, bonke bathandaza ngamxhelo mnye, besithi: “Nkosi, Mdali wezulu nomhlaba nolwandle nazo zonke izinto ezilapho,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> uDavide, isicaka sakho, ukhokho wethu, eqhutywa nguMoya oyiNgcwele wathi: “ ‘Kungani na iintlanga zisenza imbudumbudu nje? Kungani na ukuba abantu benze amayelenqe azé nje?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Iikumkani neziphathamandla zelizwe zahlangana, zavukela iNkosi *noKrestu wayo!’",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Kuba ngenene uHerode noPilato bahlangana kwesi sixeko kunye neentlanga, namaSirayeli, ngaye uYesu isiCaka sakho osinyulileyo, uMthanjiswa wakho.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bahlangana ukuze bakwenze konke owawuselukumisele ngegunya nentando yakho ukuba kuya kwenzeka.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kalokunje, Nkosi, zigqale izoyikiso zabo; thina zicaka zakho usenze siluthethe udaba lwakho ngesibindi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Philisa ngesandla sakho, unike amandla okuba imimangaliso nemiqondiso yenzeke ngegunya legama lesiCaka sakho osinyulileyo uYesu.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bakuba begqibile ukuthandaza, indawo ababehlangene kuyo yazanya-zanyiswa. Bonke bazaliswa nguMoya oyiNgcwele, baza baluthetha udaba lukaThixo benobuganga.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ewonke amakholwa ayevana entliziyo-nye. Akukho bani wayekubanga oko anako, kuba babesabelana ngezinto zonke abanazo.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> *Abathunywa babezingisa ukungqina ngovuko lweNkosi uYesu, waza uThixo wabasikelela xa bebonke.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kwakungekho bani usweleyo phakathi kwabo. Ababenemihlaba nezindlu babethengisa ngazo, baze imali leyo bayifumeneyo",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> beze nayo, bayinike abathunywa, ize yabelwe ulowo nalowo ngokweentswelo zakhe.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> UJosefu, *umLevi onkaba iseSipro, owathiywa ngabathunywa bathi nguBarnabha, uMthuthuzeli,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> wathengisa umhlaba wakhe, waza wayizisa imali leyo kubathunywa."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku kwakukho nendoda egama linguHananiya, umfazi wayo yena enguSafira. Bathengisa umhlaba wabo,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> baza inxalenye yemali leyo bayifumeneyo bayigcina, eseleyo ke bayizisa *kubathunywa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> UPetros wabuza wathi: “Hananiya, kutheni ukuba umyeke uSathana alawule intliziyo yakho, akwenze uxokise uMoya oyiNgcwele ngokugcina inxalenye yemali oyifumeneyo ngomhlaba wakho?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Umhlaba wakho ubungowakho phambi kokuba uwuthengise, nemali yawo ibiyeyakho emveni kokuba uwuthengisile. Kungani ke ukuba ufike kwisigqibo sokwenza into enje? Awuxokisanga mntu, uxokise uThixo.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Akuweva loo mazwi uHananiya wawa phantsi, wafa; baza bonke abayivayo loo nto bankwantya luloyiko.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bafika abafana, bawuthatha bawuthandela umzimba wakhe, baya kumngcwaba.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Emva kweeyure ezintathu, yafika inkosikazi kaHananiya ingekayiva loo nto ihlileyo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Wabhekisa kuyo uPetros esithi: “Khawutsho, ingaba le yimali epheleleyo eniyizuze ngokuthengisa umhlaba wenu nomyeni wakho?” Yaphendula yathi: “Ewe, iphelele.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wayibuza wathi uPetros: “Kungani ukuba wena nendoda yakho nidibane ngokuvavanya uMoya weNkosi? Uyabona ke, abafana abavela kungcwaba indoda yakho nâbo emnyango, nawe lo baza kukuthatha bemke nawe.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngoko nangoko uSafira wawa ezinyaweni zakhe, wafa. Bangena abafana, bambona ukuba ufile, bamthatha baya kumngcwaba ecaleni komyeni wakhe.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Xa lilonke ibandla nabo bonke abayivayo le nto bazaliswa kukunkwantya.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> *Abathunywa benza imiqondiso nemimangaliso emininzi ebantwini. Bonke abakholwayo babehlangana eVarandeni kaSolomon.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Abangakholwayo babengazibandakanyi nabo, nakuba kwakuthethwa kakuhle ngabo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kuyo yonke loo nto kwabakho ihlokondiba lamadoda namakhosikazi azinikelayo eNkosini, laza longezeka inani labo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Baza abagulayo basiwa ezitalatweni, balaliswa ezibhedini nasemakhukweni, ukuze kuthi xa agqithayo uPetros isithunzi sakhe siwe phezu kwabanye.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Izihlwele zabantu zazisiza, zivela kwiidolophu ezimelene neJerusalem, zizisa abagulayo nâbo babeneendimoni, baze baphile bonke.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Umbingeleli omkhulu nabalingane bakhe, abo beqela *labaSadusi, babamonela *abathunywa,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> baza bababamba babafaka entolongweni.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kwangobo busuku isithunywa seNkosi sawavula amasango entolongo, sabakhokelela phandle abathunywa, sathi kubo:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Hambani niye *endlwini kaThixo, nibafundise yonke into abantu ngale ntlalo intsha.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bevile ke abathunywa, bathi kwasekuseni bangena endlwini kaThixo, bafundisa. Umbingeleli omkhulu nabalingane bakhe nabo bonke abadala bamaJuda, babiza intlanganiso epheleleyo *yeBhunga, baza bathumela entolongweni ukuba abathunywa beziswe phambi kwabo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Zifikile izigidimi azibafumananga abathunywa entolongweni; zabuya ke zeza kuxela entlanganisweni, zathi:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Intolongo siyifumene ivalwe ngokuqinileyo, nabalindi bewagcinile amasango, kodwa sakuwavula amasango, asifumananga mntu ngaphakathi.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kwathi intloko yabalindi bendlu kaThixo nababingeleli abaziintloko bakuyiva le nto, baxakwa ukuba ngaba kuhle ntoni na kubathunywa.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kwafika ndoda ithile eyathi kubo: “Khangelani, amadoda ebeniwafake entolongweni nangaya efundisa abantu endlwini kaThixo!”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Yasuka ke intloko yabalindi yahamba nabaphantsi kwayo, babaphuthuma abathunywa. Babaphatha kakuhle abathunywa, kuba besoyika hleze baxulutywe ngamatye ngabantu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Babazisa phambi kweBhunga abathunywa, waza umbingeleli omkhulu wabamangalela esithi:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Saninika imiyalelo engqongqo yokuba ningaphindi nifundise egameni lale ndoda; kodwa khanikhangele into eniyenzileyo! Imfundiso yenu niyisarhaze kule Jerusalem iphela; ngoku nifuna ukuxhoma ukufa kwayo phezu kwethu.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> OoPetros baphendula bathi: “Asinakwenza nto yimbi; sifanele ukuthobela uThixo endaweni yabantu!",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> UThixo woobawo bethu wamvusa uYesu ekufeni, ekubeni nina nambulalayo ngokumxhoma emnqamlezweni.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> UThixo wammisela ewongeni, wayiNkokheli noMsindisi wokunika amaSirayeli ithuba lokuguquka, aze axolelwe izono zawo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Thina noMoya oyiNgcwele osisipho sikaThixo kwabo bamthobelayo, singamangqina azo ezi zinto.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Akuweva la mazwi amalungu eBhunga avutha ngumsindo kangangokuba afuna ukuba babulawe abathunywa.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kodwa omnye wabo, *owayengumFarasi ogama linguGamaliyeli, owayengumchazi-mthetho ohloniphekileyo kubantu bonke, waphakama wayalela ukuba abathunywa khe bakhutshelwe phandle.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Wabhekisa eBhungeni esithi: “MaSirayeli, yilumkeleni into eniyenzayo kula madoda.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ngaphambi koku kukhe kwavela uTuda ezenza uthile obalulekileyo, waza walandelwa ngamadoda akwisithuba samakhulu amane. Kodwa wafa, abalandeli bakhe bathi saa, waza naloo mbutho wakhe wafa.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Emva koko kwavela uJuda umGalili, ngexesha lobalo, naye walandelwa ngabantu abaninzi, kodwa naye wafa, nabalandeli bakhe basarhaka.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ngokunjalo nakwesi isihlandlo musani ukuthatha manyathelo ngakula madoda. Wayekeni, kuba ukuba lo msebenzi wawo yinto nje yabantu uza kuphelela esithubeni;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> ukanti ukuba yinto evela kuThixo, aninako ukuwutshabalalisa. Endaweni yaloo nto ningazibhaqa nisilwa noThixo.” IBhunga lalandela icebo likaGamaliyeli.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Baza ke bababiza abathunywa, babayala ukuba bangaze baphinde bathethe ngegama likaYesu. Emva koko ke bakatswa abathunywa, baza bakhululwa.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Abathunywa balishiya iBhunga elo benemincili, kuba uThixo ebafumanise befanelekile ukuba bahlazeke ngenxa yegama likaYesu.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bazingisa ke imihla yonke, endlwini kaThixo nasemakhayeni, ukufundisa nokushumayela iindaba ezimnandi ezingoYesu onguKrestu."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kwathi kwakubon' ukuba liyanda inani labalandeli bakaYesu, kwavela ukungevisisani phakathi kwamaJuda athetha isiGrike kwanamaJuda athetha olweenkobe. AmaJuda athetha isiGrike akhalazela ukuba abahlolokazi bawo àbamkeliswa kakuhle kwimali yenkxaso yemihla ngemihla.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> *Abathunywa abalishumi elinambini balihlanganisa ibandla lilonke, bathi kulo: “Asinto intle kuthi ukuba sikuyekelele ukushumayela ilizwi likaThixo ngenxa yokuzixakekisa ngomsebenzi wokwabela abasweleyo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngoko ke, mawethu, khethani amadoda abe sixhenxe phakathi kwenu, awaziwa ngokuzaliswa nguMoya oyiNgcwele nangobulumko; thina ke siwamisele kulo msebenzi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngalinye ke, thina siya kuzinikela ngokupheleleyo kumsebenzi wokushumayela nasemithandazweni.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Isiphakamiso sabathunywa samkeleka kubo bonke; baza ke banyula aba: uStefano, indoda ezele lukholo nanguMoya oyiNgcwele, noFilipu, noProkuro, noNikano, noTimon, noParmena, kwakunye noNikolawo waseAntiyokwe owayengumngeni-buJudeni.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Aba ke banikelwa kubathunywa, baza bona babamisela ngokubathandazela nokubabeka izandla.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Laya lisanda ke ilizwi likaThixo, laza ke nenani labalandeli bakaYesu lakhula kakhulu eJerusalem, kwabakho neqela lababingeleli elazinikelayo eNkosini.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UStefano, indoda eyayisikelelwe nguThixo, izele ngamandla, wênza imiqondiso nemimangaliso phakathi kwabantu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Aza amadoda athile amchasa. Wona ayedla ngokuhlangana *endlwini yesikhungo ekuthiwa yeyamakhoboka akhululekileyo. AyengamaJuda avela eKirene naseAlesandriya. Wona namaJuda aseKiliki nawaseAsiya axambulisana noStefano.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kodwa uMoya wamnika ubulumko uStefano, ngokokude bangabi nako ukuphikisana naye.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Baza ke bafunza amadoda athile, khon' ukuze athi: “Thina simve ethetha kakubi ngoMosis nangoThixo.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngale ndlela bamenza wavukelwa ngabantu, nangabadala, nangabachazi-mthetho. Bamqubula uStefano, bamthatha bamsa entlanganisweni *yeBhunga.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bezisa namanye amadoda athetha ubuxoki ngaye, athi: “Le ndoda isoloko ithetha ngokuchaseneyo *nendlu kaThixo *nangomthetho kaMosis.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kuba samva esithi lo Yesu waseNazarete uya kuyitshabalalisa indlu kaThixo, awatshintshe namasiko esawafumana kuMosis.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bonke abo babehleli entlanganisweni bamthi ntsho ngamehlo uStefano, baza babubona ubuso bakhe bunjengobesithunywa sezulu."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Umbingeleli omkhulu wabhekisa kuStefano wathi: “Khanyela watyholwa!”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Waza uStefano wathetha nentlanganiso wenjenje: “Mawethu nani bobawo, khanindiphulaphule. UThixo, eyona ngangalala, wabonakala kukhokho wethu uAbraham ngexesha awayehlala eMesopotami, ngaphambi kokuba aye kuhlala eHaran,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> wathi kuye: ‘Suka, umke apha, uzishiye izizalwana zakho, kunye nelizwe lakowenu, uye kumhlaba endiya kukubonisa wona.’",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Waza ke ngoko wawushiya umhlaba wamaKaledi, waya kuhlala eHaran. Emveni kokufa kukayise, uThixo wathi uAbraham makafudukele kweli lizwe nikulo nani ngoku.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngelo xesha uThixo akamnikanga nendawana le uAbraham kulo mhlaba, ukuba ayime: hayi, nditsho nomhlathana lo womhlaba! Kodwa kananjalo uThixo wamthembisa uAbraham ukuba uya kumnika loo mhlaba, awume yena nezizukulwana zakhe emva kwakhe. Ukusenza kwakhe uThixo esi sithembiso uAbraham wayengekazali mntwana.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> UThixo wathetha ngolu hlobo kuye: ‘Isizukulwana sakho siya kufuduka, siye kuhlala elizweni lasemzini, apho siya kuba ngamakhoboka, sibandezeleke iminyaka engamakhulu amane.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kodwa mna ndiya kubagweba abo bantu siphantsi kwabo; kuze kuthi emva kwelo thuba, babuye kwelo lizwe, beze kundikhonza kule ndawo.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Waza uThixo wamnika ulwaluko uAbraham ukutywina loo mnqophiso. UAbraham ke wamolùsa uIsake ngosuku lwesibhozo ezelwe, waza ngokukwanjalo uIsake wamolùsa uYakobi, noYakobi wenza kwaloo nto kookhokho abalishumi elinambini.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Oobawo bammonela uJosefu, bamthengisa waba likhoboka eJiputa. Kodwa uThixo waba naye,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> wamweza kuzo zonke iinkxwaleko awaba kuzo. Akusiwa phambi kokumkani waseJiputa, uThixo wamenza wathandeka uJosefu, wampha nobulumko. Ukumkani wammisela uJosefu wayirhuluneli yelaseJiputa nekomkhulu lakhe.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kwabakho indlala enkulu kulo lonke elaseJiputa nelaseKanana, ababi nakufumana nokutya oku ookhokho, ikati ilele eziko.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Akuva uYakobi ukuba eJiputa kukho ukudla, wabathumela okokuqala oonyana bakhe; ngookhokho kuthi ke abo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kutyelelo lwabo lwesibini uJosefu wazazisa kubantakwabo, waza wamxelela ukumkani ngamawabo lawo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> UJosefu wamema uyise uYakobi ukuba aye kuhlala eJiputa nomzi wakhe wonke. Babengamashumi asixhenxe anesihlanu bebonke.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Wehla ke uYakobi, waya eJiputa, apho yena nookhokho bethu bafela khona.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Imizimba yabo yasiwa eShekem, apho yangcwatywa kwingcwaba elathengwa nguAbraham koonyana bakaHamori.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Ekusondeleni kwexesha lokuba uThixo asizalisekise isithembiso awasenza kuAbraham, abantu bakuthi ababeseJiputa babesebande kakhulu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ekuhambeni kwethuba kwavela kumkani wumbi, owayengamazi uJosefu, wangumlawuli weJiputa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Wabenzela ubutshijolo abantu bakowethu, wabakhohlakalela ookhokho bethu, ebanyanzela ukuba babalahle abantwana babo, ukuze babe sesichengeni sokufa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Wazalwa ngeli xesha ke uMosis engumntwana omhle kakhulu. Wakhuliselwa ekhayeni lakhe iinyanga ezintathu;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> waza wathi naye akulahlwa, wacholwa yintombi yokumkani waseJiputa, yazikhulisela yena.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Wabufunda bonke ubulumko bamaJiputa, waza waba yingcaphephe ekuthetheni nasekwenzeni.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Akuba neminyaka engamashumi amane uMosis, watyelela amawabo amaSirayeli.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Wabona uwabo edlakathiswa ngumJiputa, waza wamnceda, waphindezela ngokumbulala umJiputa lowo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Wayecinga ukuba amawabo oqonda ukuba uThixo ufuna ukusebenzisa yena ekuwakhululeni, kodwa akazange aqonde.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngenye imini wagagana namaSirayeli amabini esilwa, waza wazama ukuwohlula, esithi kuwo: ‘Khangelani, madoda, niyazalana; kungani ukuba nilwe ke?’",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kodwa lo wayevuyelela omnye, watyhalela uMosis bucala, wabuza wathi: ‘Ngubani okwenze induna nomgwebi phezu kwethu?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Nam ufuna ukundibulala njengalaa mJiputa umbuleleyo izolo?’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Akuyiva le ntetho uMosis, wabaleka, waya kuhlala kumhlaba waseMidiyan. Apho wazala oonyana ababini.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> “Emva kwamashumi amane eminyaka, kwabonakala isithunywa seNkosi kuMosis sisemalangatyeni etyholo elivuthayo entlango ngakwintaba yeSinayi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Lo mbono wammangalisa uMosis, wasondela etyholweni apho ukuba aliqwalasele. Suka weva ilizwi leNkosi lisithi:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ‘Mna ndinguThixo wookhokho bakho, uThixo ka-Abraham, kaIsake, noYakobi.’ UMosis wankwantya kukoyika, akabi saba nako ukulikhangela.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> INkosi yathi kuye: ‘Khulula iimbadada ezo, kuba indawo le umi kuyo ingcwele.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ndiyibonile ingcinezelo nentlupheko yabantu bam eJiputa; ndisivile isikhalo sabo; ke ngoku ndize kubahlangula. Yiza ke, ndikuthume eJiputa.’",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Lo ngulaa Mosis ambukulayo amaSirayeli esithi: ‘Ngubani okwenze induna nomgwebi phezu kwethu?’ Kanti ke lo Mosis unguyena mntu uThixo amthume ukuba abe ngumlawuli nomsindisi, esebenzisa isithunywa sezulu eso uMosis wasibona etyholweni elivuthayo.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Wabakhokela ke abantu ukuphuma eJiputa, wenza imiqondiso nemimangaliso, eJiputa nakuLwandle oluBomvu, kananjalo nasentlango, iminyaka emashumi mane.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Nguloo Mosis wathi kumaSirayeli: ‘UThixo uya kunithumela *umshumayeli ophuma kwalapha kumawenu njengam.’",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Nguye lowa wayekunye nebandla likaSirayeli entlango. Wayekhona apho nookhokho bethu, ekwakunye nesithunywa sezulu esasithetha naye entabeni yeSinayi. Wamkela kuThixo imiyalelo ephilileyo ukuba ayidlulisele kuthi.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> “Kananjalo ookhokho bethu bala ukumthobela, bambukula, besithi kubhetele baphindele kwaseJiputa.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kungoko bathi kuAron: ‘Senzele *oothixo bokusikhokela, kuba asiyazi into emngeneyo laa Mosis wasikhupha eJiputa.’",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Kungeli thuba ke apho baziqingqela umfanekiso wethole, baza balenzela umbingelelo, benza netheko lokuzivuyisa ngenxa yaloo nto yayenziwe zizandla zabo.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ngenxa yaloo nto uThixo wabafulathela, wabayeka ukuba banqule iinkwenkwezi zezulu, njengoko kubhaliweyo encwadini *yabashumayeli kwathiwa: “ ‘MaSirayeli, yayingendim enanimxhelela, nimenzela amadini, iminyaka emashumi mane entlango.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> *Yayisisibingelo *sesithixo *uMoleki enanisiphethe, nomfanekiso wenkwenkwezi yesithixo *uRefani. Zizithixo enazenzayo, khon' ukuze nizinqule. Ngoku ke ndiya kunigxothela ngaphaya kweBhabheli.’",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> “Ookhokho bethu bona babenaso entlango *isibingelelo esingqina ubukho bukaThixo. Sasakhiwe ngokomfanekiselo lowo uThixo wawubonisa uMosis.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Emva koko ookhokho bethu abasamkelayo isibingelelo kooyise, bahamba naso, kwada kwaza kuthi gaa ngexesha likaYoshuwa, xeshikweni bawuthathayo umhlaba wezizwe abazigxothelwa nguThixo. Sahlala ke isibingelelo eso kwada kwayimihla kaDavide.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Yena wathandeka kuThixo, waza wacela ukuba uThixo amvumele akhele inzala kaYakobi indlu yokunqula.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Kodwa yona indlu leyo yakhiwa nguSolomon.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> “Phofu yena uThixo uPhezukonke akahlali zindlwini zakhiwe ngabantu; njengoko atshoyo umshumayeli:",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> “ ‘Izulu likomkhulu lam,’ itsho iNkosi: ‘Umhlaba wona ngamathânga am. Ndluni eningaze nindakhele yona? Iphi yona indawo endingaphumla kuyo?",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Ezi zinto azenziwanga ndim zonke na?’",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> “Bantundini baneenkani, abantliziyo ziqaqadekileyo, hayi ubuthulu benu emyalelweni kaThixo! Nifuz' ooyihlo! Nani nasoloko nimgiba uMoya oyiNgcwele!",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Nguwuphi umshumayeli abangamtshutshisanga ooyihlo? Bazibulala izigidimi zikaThixo, ezathi kwangaphambili zakuvakalisa ukuza kwalowo uliLungisa. Kungokunje nimngcatshile namgebenga.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Umthetho kaThixo owaziswa zizithunywa zezulu, wamkelwa nini kanye – kodwa anikawuthobeli unangoku!”",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Athi amalungu *eBhunga akuziva ezi zinto zithethwa nguStefano, acaphuka kangangokuba ade abe ngathi osuka amthi qwenge-qwenge.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Kodwa uStefano yena ezele nguMoya oyiNgcwele, wakhangela ezulwini, waza wabubona ubuqaqawuli bukaThixo, noYesu emi ewongeni ngakuThixo.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Waqhuba wathi: “Khawukhangele! Amazulu ndiwabona evulekile, *noNyana woLuntu emile ngasekunene kukaThixo!”",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Kwesi sithuba basuka bazivingca iindlebe zabo, bahlahlamba kwathi nkxwe, baza basuka indulumbane phezu kwakhe.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Bamkhuphela ngaphandle kwedolophu, bamxuluba ngamatye. Abamangaleli bakaStefano bazigcinisa iimpahla zabo kumfana ogama linguSawule.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Bemxuluba njalo ngamatye, uStefano yena wakhala eNkosini esithi: “Nkosi Yesu, wamkele umoya wam!”",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Waguqa ngamadolo, wadanduluka wathi: “Nkosi, musa ukubabeka tyala ngesi sono!” Akukhov' ukutsho, wafa ke."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Naye uSawule wabuthakazelela obu bugebenga. Kwangaloo mhla kwaqaleka intshutshiso enkulu ebandleni laseJerusalem. Ngaphandle *kwabathunywa, basarhazeka bonke abakholwayo, kuwo onke amaphondo elakwaJuda naseSamariya.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amadoda athile anenzondelelo amngcwaba uStefano enesingqala esikhulu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kwangelo lixa uSawule yena wazama ukulitshabalalisa ibandla, engena kwiminyango ngeminyango, ebarhuqa abakholwayo, amadoda kwanabafazi, ebavalela entolongweni.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Abakholwayo ababethe saa, bahamba bezishumayela iindaba ezimnandi kulo lonke.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> UFilipu yena waya kwidolophana yaseSamariya, wamshumayela uKrestu kubantu ababelapho,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> baza bamphulaphula ngomdla omkhulu bemxhelo mnye. Bathi bemphulaphula, baba beyibona nemiqondiso awayeyenza.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Iindimoni zazikhutshwa ebantwini, zisitsho ngesikhalo esikhulu. Abafe umzimba neziqhwala babephiliswa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ezi zinto zatsho abantu baloo dolophu banovuyo olukhulu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kuloo dolophu kwakukho indoda egama linguSimon, owayesenethuba elide esenza izimanga phakathi kwamaSamariya ngemilingo yakhe. Wayezenza uthile obalulekileyo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Zaye iindidi zonke zabantu kuloo dolophu zimhlonela. Babesithi unamandla obuthixo, bembiza ngokuthi nguMandla-makhulu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Babemhlonele kuba wayesebamangalise ixesha elide ngemilingo yakhe.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kodwa bathi bakukholwa yintshumayelo kaFilipu yeendaba ezimnandi ezingolawulo lukaThixo oluthwasileyo negama likaYesu Krestu, kwabhaptizwa amadoda kwanamakhosikazi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> NoSimon wakholwa, waza akuba ebhaptiziwe akahlukana noFilipu, ekhwankqiswa yimimangaliso nemiqondiso awayeyenza uFilipu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bathi bakuva *abathunywa eJerusalem ukuba abantu baseSamariya balamkele ilizwi likaThixo, bathumela uPetros noYohane khona.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bakufika khona babathandazela abakholwayo ukuba bamkele uMoya oyiNgcwele,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> kuba wayengekabafikeli uMoya oyiNgcwele; nto nje babebhaptizelwe egameni leNkosi uYesu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Aba bantu bamamkela uMoya oyiNgcwele, bakuba ooPetros noYohane bebabeke izandla.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> USimon akubona ukuba bamkele uMoya oyiNgcwele, bakubekwa izandla ngabathunywa, wafuna ukubanika imali ooPetros noYohane,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> esithi: “Nam ndipheni la mandla; khon' ukuze nabani na endimbeke izandla afumane uMoya oyiNgcwele.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Waphendula wathi uPetros: “Hamb' uye kufa kunye naloo mali yakho, kuba ucinga ukuba isipho sesisa sikaThixo singathengwa ngemali!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Akunanxaxheba kulo msebenzi wethu, kuba iingcinga zakho azilunganga phambi koThixo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Guquka kule nkohlakalo yakho, uthandaze ukuba uThixo akuxolele ngale nto inje,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> kuba ndiyabona ukuba unekratshi elilizothe, waye ulikhoboka lokungcola.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Uthe ke uSimon kooPetros noYohane: “Ndincedeni, zinkosi, nindithandazele eNkosini ukuze zingandihleli zonke ezi zinto nizithethileyo.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Emveni kokuba benike ubungqina beluthetha udaba lweNkosi kwabo bantu, uPetros noYohane bagoduka, baya eJerusalem. Endleleni yabo egodukayo bazishumayela iindaba ezimnandi kwiilali ezininzi zaseSamariya.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ke kaloku kwathetha isithunywa seNkosi noFilipu, sathi: “Zilungiselele uhle ngendlela esentlango esuka eJerusalem iye eGaza.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Waxhabasha ke waya uFilipu. Endleleni apho wadibana nendoda elithenwa. Lo mfo wayengunondyebo wokumkanikazi uKhandase waseTopiya. Wayegoduka ngenqwelo, evela kunqula uThixo eJerusalem. Enqwelweni apho wayehamba efunda incwadi *yomshumayeli uIsaya.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Wathi uMoya oyiNgcwele kuFilipu: “Yiya kulaa nqwelo, uhambe nayo.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> UFilipu wakhawuleza waya kuyo, waza wamva unondyebo lowo efunda encwadini yomshumayeli uIsaya, wambuza wathi: “Uyayilandela na le nto uyifundayo?”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Waphendula wathi: “Ndingathini ukuyilandela kungekho bani undichazelayo?” Watsho wacela uFilipu ukuba akhwele enqwelweni ahambe naye.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Nasi isicatshulwa seziBhalo awayesifunda: “Wafana negusha eya kuxhelwa, wafana netakane elithe cwaka lichetywa, naye wathula wathi tu.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ekuthotyweni kwakhe akabanga namhlanguli; akukho bani uya kuchaza ngesizukulwana sakhe, kuba ubomi bakhe emhlabeni bunqanyulwe.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Unondyebo wabuza kuFilipu wathi: “Khawundixelele, uthetha ngabani apha umshumayeli? Ngaba uthetha yena siqu, okanye uthetha ngomnye umntu?”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> UFilipu wamchazela, eqalela kanye kule ndawo eziBhalweni, wamtyhilela iindaba ezimnandi ezingoYesu.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ekuhambeni kwabo bada bafika ndaweni ithile inamanzi, laza lathi ithenwa: “Nanga amanzi, kungani ukuba ndingàbhaptizwa?” [",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Waphendula wathi uFilipu: “Ungábhaptizwa ukuba uyakholwa ngentliziyo yakho yonke.” Lathi ke lona: “Ndiyakholwa ukuba uYesu Krestu nguNyana kaThixo.”]",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> UmTopiya lowo wathi makumiswe, waza yena noFilipu bangena emanzini, uFilipu wambhaptiza.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bakuphuma emanzini apho, uMoya weNkosi wamthatha wemka naye uFilipu. UmTopiya lowo akabanga sambona uFilipu, kodwa wayihamba indlela yakhe leyo ezele luvuyo.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> UFilipu wazifumana eseAshdode, waza wazihamba zonke ezo dolophu eshumayela iindaba ezimnandi, wada waya kufika eKhesariya."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngalo lonke eli thuba uSawule yena wayefutha izisongelo zokwenzakalisa abalandeli beNkosi. Waya kumbingeleli omkhulu, wacela ukuba amnike iincwadi zeziqinisekiso,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ukuze aye *ezindlwini zesikhungo zamaJuda eDamasko, abe nako ukuthi xa ebafumana abalandeli bale Ndlela yeNkosi, abakhonkxe, amadoda kunye nabafazi, eze nabo eJerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Endleleni yakhe eya eDamasko, xa asondelayo apho edolophini, ngequbuliso wabona ukukhanya esibhakabhakeni, okwasuka kwambanekela ngeenxa zonke.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Watsho wawa phantsi, waza weva ilizwi limbiza lisithi kuye: “Sawule, Sawule, unditshutshiselani na?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Yena wabuza wathi: “Wena ungubani, Nkosi?” Ilizwi elo laphendula lathi: “Mna ndinguYesu, lowo umtshutshisayo wena.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Phakama, uhambe ungene apha edolophini; uya kuyixelelwa khona into omawuyenze.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngeli xesha amadoda awayehamba noSawule ayemile, ethe cwaka, eliva lona ilizwi elo lalithetha, kodwa engaboni mntu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> USawule waphakama, wakhangela ngamehlo, kodwa akabi nako ukubona nento le. Ngoko ke abo babehamba naye bamrhola ngesandla, bangena naye eDamasko.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Waba ntsuku-ntathu eyimfama, engatyi, engaseli.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> EDamasko apho kwakukho umlandeli kaYesu ogama linguHananiya. INkosi yathetha naye embonweni, yambiza yathi: “Hananiya!” Yena wasabela wathi: “Ndilapha, Nkosi.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Yathi iNkosi kuye: “Khawuleza, uye esitalatweni ekuthiwa sesithe ngqo, uze ufune indlu kaJuda, apho kuyo ukhangele indoda yaseTarso egama linguSawule. Iyathandaza khona,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> futhi embonweni wayo ibone indoda egama linguHananiya, ingena ibeka izandla phezu kwayo, ukuze iphinde ibe nokubona.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Waphendula wathi uHananiya: “Nkosi, baninzi abantu abandixeleleyo ngale ndoda, nangezinto ezilumezayo ezenzileyo ebantwini bakho eJerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nangoku ilapha eDamasko nje, inamagunya ewathathe kubabingeleli abaziintloko, ukuze ikhonkxe bonke abakunqulayo.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Yaza yathi iNkosi kuye: “Hamba uye kuyo, kuba mna ndiyikhethile ukuba indisebenzele, yazise igama lam kwiintlanga nakookumkani nakulo usapho lukaSirayeli.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ndaye mna ngokwam ndiya kuyibonisa ubunzima efanele ukubuva ngenxa yam.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Wahamba ke uHananiya, wangena endlwini leyo ebeyixelelwe, wambeka izandla uSawule, esithi: “Sawule, mfondini, iNkosi indithumile, uYesu ngokwakhe, lo umbonileyo endleleni, xa ubusiza apha. Indithumele ukuze wena uphinde ufumane ukubona, uzaliswe nanguMoya oyiNgcwele.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ngoko nangoko kwaba ngathi amehlo kaSawule ongulwe, waza waphinda wanako ukubona. Wathi akuvuka wabhaptizwa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Emveni kokuba etyile, wabuya wangumqabaqaba. USawule wahlala iintsukwana nabalandeli bakaYesu eDamasko.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Zisukanje waya *ezindlwini zesikhungo zamaJuda, wafika washumayela ngoYesu, esithi unguNyana kaThixo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bonke ababemva, babemangaliswa, bebuza besithi: “Ngaba le ndoda asiyiyo na leya yayibatshutshisa eJerusalem bonke abathetha ngeli gama? Kanene, andithi nangoku ilapha nje, izele ukuze ibambe abantu, ibase kubabingeleli abaziintloko?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kodwa intshumayelo kaSawule yaya ikhula emandleni, neengxoxo zakhe ezibonisa ukuba uYesu *unguKrestu, zabetha asikwa imilomo amaJuda aseDamasko.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kwakuba kudlule iintsuku ezininzi amaJuda ahlanganisana, afutha amacebo okumbulala uSawule;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> kodwa eli yelenqe waliva uSawule. Imini nobusuku babemlinda emasangweni edolophu, khon' ukuze bambulale.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ngabusuku buthile abalandeli bakaYesu bamthatha uSawule, bamthoba ngengobozi eludongeni.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> USawule waya eJerusalem, wazama ukuzibandakanya nabalandeli bakaYesu. Kodwa bonke babemoyika, bengakholwa ukuba naye ungumlandeli kaYesu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Wada wancedwa nguBharnabha owamthathayo, wamsa *kubathunywa, wabachazela indlela awabonana ngayo neNkosi, nento eyathethwayo yiNkosi kuye. Wababalisela nangokulishumayela kukaSawule ngesibindi igama likaYesu eDamasko.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Waza ke uSawule wahlala apho eJerusalem, ejikeleza elishumayela ngesibindi igama leNkosi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ngokunjalo wathetha, waxoxa nawo namaJuda athetha isiGrike, kodwa asuka afuna ukumbulala.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Athi amakholwa akuyiqonda le nto, amthatha uSawule, amsa eKhesariya, aza amthumela eTarso.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ke kaloku ibandla kulo lonke elakwaJuda naseGalili naseSamariya lazola, kungekho ntshutshiso. Laba nenkqubela, lakhula nangamanani, limhlonela uThixo, likhuthazwa nguMoya oyiNgcwele.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Njengoko uPetros wayeyihamba yonke loo ngingqi, ngathuba lithile watyelela abantu bakaThixo eLida.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Apho wahlangana nendoda egama linguEneya. Yayife icala, futhi ineminyaka esibhozo yalalayo.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Wathi uPetros kuyo: “Eneya, uYesu Krestu uyakuphilisa. Phakama, wendlule umandlalo wakho.” Ngakonje ukuba atsho, wavuka uEneya.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bathi bakumbona, bonke abantu ababehlala eLida nakwintili yaseSharon bazinikela eNkosini.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> EJopa kwakukho umlandeli kaYesu ogama linguTabhita, oko kukuthi uBhadikazi. Lonke ixesha lakhe wayelichithela ekwenzeni okulungileyo, enezinwe, ebanceda abahlelelekileyo.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ngeli xesha wagula, wasweleka. Bawuhlamba umzimba wakhe, bawubeka egumbini elikumgangatho ophezulu.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Njengoko iJopa yayingekude eLida, beva abalandeli bakaYesu ukuba uPetros useLida, baza bathumela amadoda amabini nomyalezo wokuba uPetros makancede afike ngokukhawuleza.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Akalibazisanga uPetros; wahamba nawo kwangoko. Akufika khona, wasiwa egumbini elo liphezulu, waphahlwa libubu labahlolokazi ababelila, bembonisa iingubo kwaneempahla awayezenza uBhadikaziNqesiGrike “uDorkas” esaphilile.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> UPetros wabakhuphela phandle bonke, waza waguqa wathandaza. Wathi kamva waguqukela kuso isidumbu, wathi: “Tabhita, vuka!” Wajonga, waza akubona uPetros, wavuka.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Wasondela kuye uPetros, wamncedisa, waphakama. Wawabiza ke uPetros amakholwa kunye nabahlolokazi abo, wamnikela kubo ephilile.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ezi ndaba zafikelela kuyo yonke iJopa, baza abantu abaninzi bazinikela eNkosini.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> UPetros waba neentsuku ezininzi ehleli apho eJopa kunye nendoda egama linguSimon, umsuki weemfele."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> EKhesariya kwakukho umphathi-butho wamajoni aseRoma ogama linguKorneli. Umkhosi wakhe kwakusithiwa ngowaseItali.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Yena nosapho lwakhe babengabantu abamnqulayo bemhlonela uThixo. Wayengumntu onezinwe, ewanceda amaJuda ahlelelekileyo, ethandaza rhoqo kuThixo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngenye injika-langa kwisithuba sentsimbi yesithathu, waba nombono, wasibona ngokucacileyo isithunywa sikaThixo singena sisithi kuye: “Korneli!”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wasiqwalasela enoloyiko, wathi: “Yintoni, Nkosi?” Saphendula sathi: “UThixo uyamkele imithandazo nemisebenzi yakho yesisa; akazange wakulibala.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngoku ke thuma amadoda eJopa, kumntu othile ogama linguSimon Petros,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> olundwendwe lukaSimon umsuki weemfele, ondlu ingaselwandle.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sakumka isithunywa eso, uKorneli wabiza izicaka zakhe ezibini, kunye nejoni elalimhlonela uThixo, elalingumlindi wakhe.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Wabachazela konke okwakumhlele, waza wabathuma eJopa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngomhla olandelayo, xa babesendleleni, besondela eJopa, uPetros uthe emini emaqanda waya kuthandaza phezu kwendlu kwindawo esabuvaranda.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wasuka walamba, wafuna into etyiwayo, kwathi besamlungiselela ukutya wabona umbono.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Wabona izulu livulekile, kusihla into engathi lilaphu elikhulu libanjwe ngamasondo omane, lisiza emhlabeni.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kulo kwakukho zonke iintlobo zezidalwa ezingatyiwayo ezizitho zine, ezirhubuluzayo, nezibhabhayo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Weva ilizwi lisithi kuye: “Vuka, xhela utye, Petros.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Waphendula wathi: “Nkosi, ngunotshe lowo! Mna andizange ndiyitye into engatyiwayo.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Laphinda ilizwi elo lavakala kuye lisithi: “Musa ukuthi ayityiwa into athi uThixo iyatyiwa.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Le nto yenzeka kwada kwakathathu, laza ke ilaphu elo lanyuselwa ezulwini.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ngoku asamangalisiweyo yena uPetros ukuba ngaba yintoni na intsingiselo yalo mbono, wona amadoda athunywe nguKorneli ayesede awufumana umkhondo wendlu kaSimon, selemi esangweni.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Abuzisa ukuba ngaba akukho mhambi ugama linguSimon Petros na apho.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> UPetros yena wayesajika-jikana nalo mbono ukuva kwakhe uMoya oyiNgcwele esithi: “Phulaphula, nango amadoda amathathu ekufuna.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Phakama uye kuwo la madoda, ungathandabuzi, uhambe nawo, kuba athunywe ndim.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Waya kuwo uPetros, wafika wathi: “Ndim lo nimfunayo. Ngaba nindifuna ngani?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Wona aphendula athi: “Sithunywa yiNkosi yethu uKorneli, oyindoda elungileyo emhlonelayo uThixo, ehlonitshwayo nangamaJuda. Uxelelwe sisithunywa sikaThixo ukuba makakubize uye endlwini yakhe, ukuze eve loo nto uya kumxelela yona.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Wangena nabo endlwini uPetros, baza balalisa apho ngaloo mini. Ngosuku olulandelayo wahamba nawo la madoda kunye namanye amakholwa aseJopa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngengomso wagaleleka eKhesariya, apho wafika elindelwe nguKorneli nezizalwana nezihlobo zakhe ezisenyongweni.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Xa angenayo uPetros, uKorneli wazikhahlela phambi kwakhe,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> kodwa uPetros wamphakamisa wathi: “Hayi, ndingumntu nje nam; musa ukwenjenjalo.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> UPetros wayethetha noKorneli ekungeneni kwakhe endlwini, apho wafika kubuthelene abantu abaninzi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Uthe kubo uPetros: “Nina ngokwenu nazi kakuhle ukuba umJuda akavumelekile ngokwenkolo yakowabo ukuba andwendwele nokuba abe nento yokwenza neentlanga. Selendibonisile ke kodwa uThixo ukuba mandingathathi bani njengongahlambulukanga.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Yiyo loo nto uthe wakundibiza andala. Khawundixelele ke, undibizele ntoni?”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Uthe ukuphendula uKorneli: “Ngoku kusemva kweentsuku ezine oko ndandithandaza endlwini yam, malunga neli lixa ngentsimbi yesithathu emva kwemini, kwathi gqi umfo onxibe ezibengezelayo, wema phambi kwam,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> wathi kum: ‘Korneli, uThixo uyamkele imithandazo yakho, wayikhumbula nemisebenzi yakho yesisa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ngoko ke thuma umntu eJopa, aye kubiza umntu ogama linguSimon Petros. Ulundwendwe lukaSimon umsuki weemfele, ondlu ingaselwandle.’",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ndithumele kwangoko kuwe, nawe ke ulungisile ukuza. Thina sonke sihlangene apha ngenjongo yokudibana noThixo, silindele ukuphulaphula yonke into iNkosi ekuyalele ukuba usixelele yona.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> UPetros wathetha wenjenje: “Ngenene ndiyaqonda ngoku ukuba uThixo akamkhethi wabuso bamntu.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Nabani na, nokuba ngowaluphi na uhlanga, ukuba uyamhlonela uThixo, esenza okulungileyo, wamkelekile kuye.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Niyalwazi udaba awaluthumela kumaSirayeli, evakalisa iindaba ezimnandi zoxolo ngoYesu Krestu, oyiNkosi yabantu bonke.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Niyasazi isiganeko esenzekayo kulo lonke elakwaJuda, ukuqalela eGalili, emva kokushumayela kukaYohane ngobhaptizo.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Nivile ngoYesu waseNazarete owathanjiswa nguThixo ngoMoya oyiNgcwele waba namandla. Wayehamba kulo lonke, esenza okulungileyo, ebaphilisa bonke ababephantsi kwamandla omtyholi, kuba uThixo wayenaye.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Thina singamangqina ako konke awakwenzayo eJerusalem nakwelamaJuda. Bambulala ngokumbethelela emnqamlezweni,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> waza uThixo wamvusa ekufeni ngosuku lwesithathu.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Akazange wabonakala kubantu bonke, koko wabonakala kuthi mangqina awawakhetha kwangaphambili uThixo, thina sasisitya sisela kunye naye emveni kokuba uThixo emvusile ekufeni.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Wasigunyazisa ukuba sishumayele ebantwini, singqine ukuba ungulowo uThixo amnyulele ukuba ngumgwebi wabahleliyo nabafileyo.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bâthetha ngaye bonke *abashumayeli besithi wonke umntu ozinikelayo kuye uxolelwa izono zakhe ngamandla egama lakhe.”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Esathethanje uPetros, wehla uMoya oyiNgcwele phezu kwabo bonke abo babephulaphule.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> AmaJuda akholwayo, lawo ayesuke noPetros eJopa, amangaliswa kukuba uThixo ezinike isipho soMoya oyiNgcwele neentlanga,",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> kuba baziva zithetha ngalwimi zimbi, zidumisa uThixo. UPetros wathetha wathi:",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> “Aba bantu bamkele uMoya oyiNgcwele njengoko samamkelayo nathi. Ngenene ke akukho namnye umntu ongalayo ukuba aba bantu babhaptizwe ngamanzi.”",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> UPetros ke ngoko wathi mababhaptizwe egameni likaYesu Krestu. Ke yena bamcela ukuba akhe ahlale nabo iintsukwana."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *Abathunywa namakholwa akulo lonke elakwaJuda, eva ukuba iintlanga nazo zilamkele ilizwi likaThixo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Akubuyela eJerusalem uPetros, amaJuda angamakholwa amgxeka esithi:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Wena ubulundwendwe lwabantu abangolukiyo ngokwesiko likaMosis, usitya nokutya nabo.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ke yena uPetros wabanika inkcazelo ezeleyo, esusela ekuqaleni kwento eyehlayo. Wathi:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Ndathi ndiseJopa, ndithandaza ndabona umbono. Ndabona kusihla into engathi lilaphu elikhulu, lithotywa ngamasondo omane ezulwini, yaza kuthi ngxingxilili ngakum.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ndaqwalasela ngaphakathi kuyo, ndabona izilo nezilwanyana, iinyoka neentaka zasendle.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ndeva ilizwi lisithi kum: ‘Vuka, xhela utye, Petros.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kodwa mna ndithe: ‘Nkosi, unotshe! Andizanga ndikufake kowam umlomo ukutya okungatyiwayo.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kwakho lathi ilizwi elo: ‘Musa ukuthi ayityiwa nayiphi na into uThixo athi iyatyiwa.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Le nto yenzeka kwada kwakathathu, kwathi ekugqibeleni labuyiselwa kwasezulwini elo laphu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngaloo mzuzu kanye, nako kufika kuloo mzi ndandihlala kuwo, amadoda amathathu awayethunywe kum, evela eKhesariya.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> UMoya oyiNgcwele wathi mandihambe nawo loo madoda, ndingathingazi. Naloo makholwa mathandathu aseJopa aya kunye nam eKhesariya, safikela kwaKorneli sisonke.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> UKorneli wasixelela ngombono wakhe, apho isithunywa sezulu safika sathi kuye makathumele umntu eJopa, aye kubiza umfo ogama linguSimon Petros,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> sisithi nguye oya kubazisa indlela abaya kusindiswa ngayo yena nosapho lwakhe.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ndithe ke ndakushumayela wehla kwangoko uMoya oyiNgcwele phezu kwabo, njengoko wehlayo nakuthi kuqala.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ndatsho ndacinga ngamazwi âthethwa yiNkosi xa yayisithi: ‘UYohane wayebabhaptiza ngamanzi abantu; ke nina niza kubhaptizwa ngoMoya oyiNgcwele.’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kucace gcaa ukuba uThixo ezaa ntlanga uzinike kanye esiya sipho wasinika sona thina siyamkeleyo iNkosi uYesu Krestu. Bendingubani na ke mna ukuba ndingáde ndime phambi kwentando kaThixo?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Yabanelisa le ngxelo, baza bamdumisa uThixo, ngokuba kuthe kanti neentlanga ezi uThixo uyazinika ithuba lokuguquka, ukuze zidle ubomi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Abakholwayo basarhazwa yintshutshiso yethuba lokufa kukaStefano. Abanye baphaphatheka, baya kutsho eFenike, eSipro, naseAntiyokwe. Babeluvakalisa udaba lweNkosi kumaJuda kuphela.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kodwa abanye bamakholwa, amadoda aphuma eSipro naseKirene, aya eAntiyokwe, aluvakalisa udaba nakwiintlanga ezintetho isisiGrike, ezishumayeza iindaba ezimnandi ezingeNkosi uYesu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Amandla eNkosi ayewafukamele loo madoda, laza iqela elikhulu labantu lazinikela eNkosini.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Le nto yenzekileyo ngabo yaya kuvakala nakwibandla laseJerusalem, laza lathumela uBharnabha eAntiyokwe.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Akuba efikile khona, wabubona ububele bukaThixo ebantwini; waza wavuya wabalúleka bonke ukuba bathembeke, banyaniseke eNkosini ngeentliziyo zabo zonke.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> UBharnabha wayeyindoda elungileyo, ezele nguMoya oyiNgcwele nalukholo. Abantu abaninzi bazinikela eNkosini,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> waza ke ngoko uBharnabha waya kukhangela uSawule eTarso.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Akumfumana, waya naye eAntiyokwe. Yaba ngunyaka wonke aba babini behlala phakathi kwebandla elo, baza baqeqesha iqela elikhulu. Kwakulapha eAntiyokwe apho abalandeli bakaYesu baqala ukubizwa ngokuba ngamaKrestu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ngelo xesha kwesuka *abashumayeli abathile eJerusalem baya eAntiyokwe.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Omnye wabo ogama linguAgabho, ezele nguMoya oyiNgcwele, wayixela kwangaphambili indlala eyayiza kubakho kuwo wonke umhlaba. Yona ke yafika ngexesha *likaKhesare Klawudiyo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> AmaKrestu agqiba ekubeni ulowo nalowo kuwo makaqwebele inkxaso yamakholwa akwelakwaJuda kangangoko anako.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Le nto ke bayenza, baza ke imali leyo bayithumela kubadala bebandla ngoBharnabha noSawule."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngeli thuba naye ukumkani uHerode wabatshutshisa abathile balo ibandla.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Wambulala ngekrele uYakobi umntakwabo-Yohane.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uthe akuqonda ukuba esi senzo siwakholisile amaJuda, waqhubela phambili ngokuvalela uPetros. Le nto yenzeka ngexesha *leSidlo seZonka ezingenaGwele.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Akuba ebanjiwe uPetros, wavalelwa entolongweni. Wanikelwa ukuba alindwe ngamajoni angamaqela amane angamane. UHerode wayezimisele ukumsa ematyaleni emva *kwePasika.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Waza ke uPetros wagcinwa entolongweni apho, kodwa amaKrestu wona azingisa ukumthandazela kuThixo, lo gama avalelweyo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ke kaloku uPetros wayelele phakathi kwabalindi ababini, ebotshelelwe kubo ngamatyathanga, kukho nabagadi abalinde isango lentolongo, ngobusuku obuphambi komhla awayeza kusiwa ngawo ematyaleni nguHerode.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngebhaqo kwabonakala isithunywa seNkosi simi bhuxe apho egumbini lentolongo, kwatsho kwasemini kukukhanya. Samshukumisa uPetros, samvusa sisithi: “Khawuleza, vuka!” Ukubanje sitsho, athi xibilili amatyathanga ezandleni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Saqhuba sathi: “Bhinqa, unxibe iimbadada zakho.” Wenjenjalo ke uPetros, saza saphinda isithunywa eso sathi: “Yambatha, undilandele.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wasilandela ke uPetros, baphuma entolongweni. Wayengekaqondi ukuba iyinene le nto yenziwa sisithunywa seNkosi; wayeba uyaphupha.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Babagqitha abalindi bokuqala nabesibini, baza ekugqibeleni bafika kwisango lentsimbi elivulela edolophini. Lavuleka ngokwalo isango, baphuma ke. Bathi besehla ngesitalato sesuka see shwaka isithunywa eso.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Akuqabuka ebuthongweni uPetros wathi: “Ngoku ndiyazi ukuba ngenene le nto yinyaniso! INkosi isithumele isithunywa sayo, sandihlangula egunyeni likaHerode, nakuzo zonke izinto amaJuda ebenqwenela ukuzenza kum.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Akuyiqonda le nto yenzekileyo uPetros waya emzini kaMariya, unina kaYohane Marko. Kwakukho abantu abaninzi apho, bethandaza.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Wankqonkqoza emnyango, kwaza kwaya intombazana egama linguRoda,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> eyathi yakuliva ilizwi likaPetros, yasuka yajika ngenxa yovuyo ingamvulelanga, yaya kuxela ukuba nguPetros lo unkqonkqozayo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Unantoni na? Uyageza!” bamphikisa batsho abo babesendlwini. Kodwa yena wema ekubeni le nto iyinyaniso. Bathi ke bona: “Hayi ke, fan' ukuba sisithunywa sakhe.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> UPetros yena waphikelela enkqonkqoza, bada ngelikade bamvulela, bamangaliswa kakhulu bakuqonda ukuba kuthe kanti nguPetros ngenkqu lo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Wawangawangisa ngesandla ukuba bathi cwaka, waza ke wabachazela indlela emkhuphe ngayo iNkosi entolongweni. Wabayaleza ukuba baye kuxela le nto kuYakobi nakwamanye amakholwa, waza yena wemka waya kwenye indawo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ngengomso yaba sisiphithi-phithi kubalindi bentolongo besithi: “Yaz' ukuba uphi na uPetros?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> UHerode wathi mabamfune, kodwa abazange bamfumane. Ngoko ke abalindi bancinwa, waza uHerode wagunyazisa ukuba babulawe. Emva kwesi singaneko ke, uHerode wemka kwaJuda, waya kuhlala eKhesariya okwexeshana.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> UHerode wayengavisisani mpela nabantu baseTire nabaseSidon. Kwakuba njalo bavumelana ngokuthumela igqiza labameli. Lona laqala lavana noBlasto, induna yasebhotwe, laza langena ngaye ukudala imvisiswano. Babecela uxolo kuba ilizwe labo lalixhomekeke kummandla kaHerode ekufumaneni ukudla.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngosuku olumisiweyo uHerode wavatha ezobukumkani, waza wahlala esihlalweni sakhe apho ebhotwe, wathetha nabantu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Asimntu, nguThixo lowo uthethayo,” bamemeza batsho abantu.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ngakonje ukuba batsho abantu, isithunywa seNkosi sambetha ngesifo uHerode, ngokuba engamnikanga mbeko uThixo. Wadliwa ziimpethu, wada wafa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Laqhubela phambili ilizwi likaThixo ukunwenwa.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> UBharnabha noSawule bawugqiba umsebenzi wabo, baza babuya eJerusalem, behamba noYohane Marko."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku ebandleni laseAntiyokwe kwakukho abashumayeli nabefundisi: uBharnabha, uSimon ekwakusithiwa nguMnyamana, uLukiyo waseKirene, uManayen owayekhuliswe noHerode irhuluneli, kunye noSawule.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ekuyikhonzeni kwabo iNkosi, bezila ukutya, uMoya oyiNgcwele wathi kubo: “Ndikhetheleni uBharnabha noSawule, ukuze benze umsebenzi endibabizele wona.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngoko ke bazila ukutya bathandaza, bababeka izandla, baza babandulula.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bakuba bethunywe nguMoya oyiNgcwele, uBharnabha noSawule behla baya eSeluki, baza ukusuka apho bahamba ngolwandle ukuya eSipro.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bathi bakufika eSalamisi, balishumayela khona ilizwi likaThixo ezindlwini zesikhungo zamaJuda. Babehamba noYohane Marko, khon' ukuze abancedise emsebenzini.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Basijikeleza ke isiqithi eso, bada bafika ePafo. Apho badibana nomfo onemilingo ogama linguBhar-yesu, umJuda owayezenza *umshumayeli.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Wayeliphakathi lerhuluneli yesiqithi eso, uSergiyo Pawulos, owayeyindoda enengqondo ekrele-krele. Irhuluneli leyo yababiza ooBharnabha noSawule, ifuna ukuphulaphula ilizwi likaThixo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kodwa lo mfo unemilingo, owayebizwa ngokuba nguElima ngesiGrike, wachasana nabo, nerhuluneli leyo wafuna ukuyiwexula elukholweni.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Waza ke ngoko uSawule, ogama limbi linguPawulos, ezaliswe nguMoya oyiNgcwele, wamjonga lo mfo,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> wathi: “Nyanandini kamtyholi, lutshabandini lobulungisa, uzele ngamaqhinga nobuqhetseba, usoloko uzama ukugqwetha inyaniso yeNkosi ngobuxoki!",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Khona ngoku iNkosi iza kukubetha, ube yimfama, futhi kuya kuba mzuzu ungakuboni ukukhanya.” Ngoko nangoko aba nkungu amehlo kaElima, wabuva ubumnyama buwavala, wajikeleza ke empampatha, efuna umntu ongamrhuqayo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ke kaloku yona irhuluneli yakuyibona loo nto, yazinikela, imangalisiwe yimfundiso emayela neNkosi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> UPawulos nababemphahlile bemka ePafo, bahamba ngenqanawe, baya kufika ePerga yasePamfili. Apha ke wahlukana nabo uYohane Marko, wabuyela eJerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Abanye bona banduluka ePerga, babheka eAntiyokwe yasePisidi. Bathi apho *ngoMhla wokuPhumla baya *kwindlu yesikhungo, bafika bahlala phantsi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kwathi zakuba zifundiwe izicatshulwa encwadini *yomthetho kaMosis *nezabashumayeli, amagosa endlu yesikhungo athumela ebacela esithi: “Mawethu, khanisiphe kowenu umphako welizwi, ukwenzela ukukhuthaza abantu.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Waphakama uPawulos, wawangawangisa ngesandla, ukuba kuthi cwaka, waza wenjenje ukuthetha: “Mawethu, maSirayeli, nani nina zintlanga zimhlonelayo uThixo, khanibeke iindlebe!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> UThixo lo unqulwa ngamaSirayeli nguye owanyula ookhokho bethu, wawenza amaSirayeli asisizwe esikhulu ngexesha ayengabaphambukeli kwelaseJiputa. Nguye owawakhupha ngamandla angummangaliso amaSirayeli eJiputa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Wawanyamezela iminyaka emashumi mane entlango.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ikwanguye owazitshabalalisayo izizwe ezisixhenxe eKanana, waza loo mhlaba wawunika abantu bakhe amaSirayeli.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Yonke loo nto yathatha isithuba esingangeminyaka engamakhulu amane anamashumi amahlanu. “Emva koko wabanika iinkokheli, zabalawula kwada kwalixesha lomshumayeli uSamweli.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bakufuna ukumkani, wabanika uSawule unyana kaKishe, wesizwe sakwaBhenjamin, waza wabalawula iminyaka engamashumi amane.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Akumsusa uSawule, uThixo wamisela uDavide wangukumkani. Nanga amazwi athethwa nguThixo ngoDavide: ‘Ndiphawule ukuba uDavide, unyana kaJese, ngulo mntu kanye ndimfunayo, umfo oya kwenza oko sukuba ndifuna kwenziwe.’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> NguYesu lo mzukulwana kaDavide wenziwe uMsindisi wamaSirayeli nguThixo njengoko wathembisayo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngaphambi kokufika kukaYesu, uYohane wawashumayeza onke amaSirayeli, esithi makaziguqule iindlela zawo aze abhaptizwe.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ekuwusongeni kwakhe uYohane umsebenzi wakhe, wathi ebantwini: ‘Nithi ndingubani? Andinguye lowo nicinga ukuba ndigunye. Khangelani yena uza emva kwam, ndaye mna andikufanele nokukhulula iimbadada ezi ezinyaweni zakhe.’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Mawethu, nzala ka-Abraham, nani nonke zintlanga zimhlonelayo uThixo, olu daba losindiso lwathunyelwa kuthi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kaloku abantu baseJerusalem, bekunye neenkokheli zabo, babengamazi, bengawaqondi namazwi abashumayeli bamandulo afundwayo ngayo yonke iMihla yokuPhumla. Kodwa bâwazalisekisa amazwi abo bashumayeli ngokumgweba uYesu.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Nangona babengasifumani isizathu sokuba agwetyelwe ukufa, bacela uPilato ukuba ambulale.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Emveni kokuzenza zonke izinto ezithethwa *ziziBhalo ngaye, bamothula emnqamlezweni, bamngcwaba.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kodwa uThixo yena wamvusa ekufeni,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> waza kwithuba leentsuku ezininzi wabonwa ngâbo wayejikeleza nabo ukusuka eGalili baye eJerusalem. Ngoku bangamangqina akhe kumaSirayeli.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Thina silapha nje, sizise iindaba ezimnandi kuni. Loo nto uThixo wayithembisa ookhokho bethu,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> uyenzele thina bayinzala yabo, ngokumvusa uYesu. Kunjengoko kubhaliweyo eNdumisweni yesibini, kwathiwa: “ ‘Ungunyana wam wena; namhlanje ndikuzele.’",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “UThixo wamvusa ekufeni. Ke ngoko akasayi kuze abole. Le nto uyithethe ngala mazwi athi: “ ‘Ndiya kuninika iintsikelelo ezizodwa eziqinisekileyo, endazithembisa uDavide.’",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Kwakhona uthi kwenye indawo: “ ‘Akuyi kusiyeka isicaka sakho esithembekileyo sibole.’",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Kuba kaloku ngexesha lakhe uDavide wayifeza injongo kaThixo, waza wafa emva koko, wangcwatywa ngakookhokho bakhe, wabola.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kodwa uYesu, evusiwe nje nguThixo, khange abole.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Yazini niqiniseke xa ninonke, mawethu, ukuba kungoYesu ukushunyayelwa kodaba lokuxolelwa kwezono. Ngokunjalo qondani ukuba wonke umntu ozinikelayo kuye uyakhululwa kuzo zonke izono, obungenako ukumkhulula kuzo *umthetho kaMosis.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Lumkani ke ngoko, hleze ihle kuni into eyathethwa ngabashumayeli, besithi:",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> “ ‘Khangelani, nina bagxeki, nimangaliswe nife; kuba umsebenzi endiwenza ngemihla yenu yinto eningayi kukholwa yiyo nokuba ubani uthe wanichazela.’”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Xa bayishiyayo intlanganiso ooPawulos noBharnabha, abantu babamema ukuba ze beze kwakhona ngoMhla wokuPhumla olandelayo, ukuze baphinde babafundise.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Emveni kokuphuma kwentlanganiso, uPawulos noBharnabha balandelwa sisihlwele samaJuda neentlanga eziguqukele ebuJudeni, baza basikhuthaza ukuba sibambelele ngenyameko kuThixo onesisa.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> NgoMhla woPhumlo olandelayo phantse wonke umntu osedolophini weza kuphulaphula ilizwi leNkosi.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Akuyibona le nkitha yabantu, amaJuda azala ngumona, amphikisa amnyelisa uPawulos.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Kodwa bona ooPawulos noBharnabha bawaxelela phandle amaJuda bathi: “Kakade bekufuneka lishunyayezwe nina kuqala ilizwi likaThixo; koko ngenxa yokuba nilibukula, niziqonda ukuba anibulungelanga ubomi obungonaphakade, siza kuniyeka, siye ezintlangeni.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Thina kaloku sanikwa lo myalelo yiNkosi: “ ‘Ndikumisele ukuba ube sisibane sokukhanyisela iintlanga, ube yindlela yokusindiswa kwalo lonke elimiweyo.’”",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Zavuya iintlanga zakukuva oku, zayidumisa iNkosi ngenxa yodaba lwayo. Abo ke babenyulelwe ukungena ebomini obungonaphakade, baguquka bangamakholwa.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Ilizwi leNkosi lanwenwa kuwo wonke loo mmandla.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Kodwa amaJuda adala uchuku, enza *abathunywa bavukelwa ngamadoda aloo dolophu aphambili kwanangabafazi abakumgangatho ophezulu entlalweni, ababemhlonela uThixo. Babatshutshisa babagxotha kuloo mmandla.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Abathunywa bavuthulula uthuli ezinyaweni, bekhalala, bemka baya eIkoniyo.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Basala abalandeli bakaYesu eAntiyokwe bezele luvuyo nanguMoya oyiNgcwele."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> NaseIkoniyo yaba sesezolo: uPawulos noBharnabha baya *endlwini yesikhungo baza bathetha kangangokuba iqela elikhulu lamaJuda neentlanga lazinikela.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kodwa amaJuda angakholwayo azixhokonxa iintlanga, azifaka umoya ombi ngakumakholwa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> *Abathunywa bahlala apho ixesha elide. Bathetha ngesibindi ngeNkosi, iNkosi ibanika amandla okwenza imiqondiso nemimangaliso, ingqina inyaniso yodaba lwabo ngesisa sayo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Inkoliso yabantu edolophini apho yathi qheke kubini: abanye baba ngakumaJuda, abanye baba ngakubathunywa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Zaza iintlanga namaJuda ndawonye neenkokheli zazimisela ukubaphatha kakubi abathunywa, zibaxulube ngamatye.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bathe bakuyiqonda le nto abathunywa, basaba baya eLikawoni, kwiidolophu zaseListra naseDerbhe nemimandla ejikelezileyo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Baza bazishumayela khona iindaba ezimnandi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Apho eListra kwakukho indoda eyazalwa isisiqhwala, ingazange yaba nako ukuhamba.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yawaphulaphula ngomdla amazwi kaPawulos. UPawulos wayithi ntshoo ngamehlo, waqonda ukuba inokholo olungayiphilisayo,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> wadanduluka wathi: “Suk' ume ngeenyawo.” Indoda leyo yatsiba yema, yahamba-hamba.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Zithe izihlwele zakuyibona le nto yenziwe nguPawulos, zakhwaza ngesiLikawoni zisithi: “Oothixo beze kuthi befana nabantu!”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> UBharnabha bamthiya bathi *nguZeyus, uPawulos bathi *nguHermes ngenxa yokuba yena wayesisithethi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ke kaloku kwakukho indlu yokunqulela uZeyus ngaphandle nje kwedolophu. Waza umbingeleli kaZeyus weza neenkunzi zeenkomo neentyatyambo esangweni ledolophu. Yena nesihlwele eso babefuna ukwenzela *abathunywa idini.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bathe abathunywa ooBharnabha noPawulos bakuyiva le nto iqhubekayo, bazikrazula iimpahla zabo, babaleka baya kuso isihlwele, bekhwaza besithi:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Madoda, yintoni le niyenzayo? Nathi singabantu; sifana nani! Size apha ukuze sivakalise iindaba ezimnandi, ukuze niguquke nijike kwezi zinto ziphuthileyo, nize kuThixo, owenza izulu, nomhlaba, nolwandle, nezinto ezilapho kuzo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Mandulo uThixo wabayeka abantu, benza ukuthanda kwabo;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> kodwa wasoloko ezibonakalisa ubukho bakhe ngezinto ezintle azenzayo. Usipha imvula nezilimo ngamaxesha afanelekileyo; usipha nokudla, iintliziyo zethu azizalise ngovuyo.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Naxa sebethethe kangako abathunywa, phantse bangabi nako ukusijika isihlwele ekubeni sibenzele idini.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kwafika iqela lamaJuda evela eAntiyokwe yasePisidi naseIkoniyo. Ekubeni ezifake umoya ombi izihlwele, ukuba zithathe icala lawo, bamxuluba ngamatye uPawulos, bamrhuqela ngaphandle kwedolophu, beba ufile.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kodwa akungqongwa ngamakholwa, wavuka, wabuyela kwasedolophini. Ngengomso wemka kunye noBharnabha, baya eDerbhe.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> UPawulos noBharnabha bazishumayela iindaba ezimnandi naseDerbhe, bafumana inkitha eyaba ngabalandeli bakaYesu. Baza ke babuyela eListra, baya eIkoniyo ukusuka apho, baya naseAntiyokwe yasePisidi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bawomeleza amakholwa, bewakhuthaza ukuba ahlale ehleli elukholweni enyanisekile, besithi ukufundisa: “Simelwe kukuthwala ubunzima thina singene phantsi kolawulo lukaThixo.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kwibandla ngalinye batyumba abadala, babanikela ngemithandazo nangozilo-kutya eNkosini ababethembele kuyo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Emveni kokutyhutyha ummandla wasePisidi, bafika ePamfili.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bashumayela udaba ePerga, baza badlulela eAtaliya.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Basuka apho ngesikhephe babuyela eAntiyokwe yaseSiriya, apho babenikelwe elugcinweni naselubabalweni lukaThixo ukuya kwenza kwabo lo msebenzi bawufezileyo ngoku.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bakufika eAntiyokwe, balihlanganisela ndawonye ibandla, babalisa ngezinto uThixo awazenza ngabo, bexela nokuba nabaziintlanga uThixo ubavulele indlela yokukholwa.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bahlala ke apho kunye namakholwa ithuba elide."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Amadoda athile asuka eJerusalem, aya eAntiyokwe afundisa amakholwa esithi akanako ukusindiswa ngaphandle kokuba olùswe *ngokomthetho kaMosis.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> UPawulos noBharnabha baba nengxoxo eshushu nabo ngalo mbandela, kwaza kwagqitywa ukuba uPawulos noBharnabha kunye nabanye baseAntiyokwe baye eJerusalem, bayokuva le ngxaki *kubathunywa nakubadala.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ke kaloku lakuba libandulule ibandla, bacanda kwelaseFenike nelaseSamariya, behamba bebalisa ngokuguquka kweentlanga; iindaba ke ezo ezawavuyisa kakhulu amakholwa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Befikile ke eJerusalem, bamkelwa libandla, abathunywa, nabadala, baza ke benza ingxelo kubo ngendlela awayebasebenzise ngayo uThixo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kodwa amakholwa athile awayekade engaweqela *labaFarasi, athi wona amakholwa aphuma ezintlangeni makoluswe awuthobele umthetho kaMosis.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Abathunywa nabadala benza intlanganiso, baphicotha lo mbandela.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Emva kwengxoxo ende, waphakama uPetros, wathi: “Mawethu, niyazi ukuba kwixesha elidlulileyo uThixo wandonyula phakathi kwenu ukuba iintlanga zizive ngam iindaba ezimnandi, zize ziguquke.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UThixo ozaziyo iintliziyo zabantu, wabonakalisa ukuzamkela iintlanga ngokuzinika uMoya oyiNgcwele njengoko wasinikayo nathi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Akabonakalisanga mahluko phakathi kwazo nathi; nazo wazihlambulula iintliziyo zakuba zizinikele kuye.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngoku ke nimlingela ntoni uThixo ngokuthwalisa amakholwa umthwalo abangazange babe nako ukuwuthwala ookhokho bethu, nathi ngokwethu esingenako ukuwuthwala?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hayi bo! Sikholwa kukuba thina sisindiswa ngesisa seNkosi uYesu kwanjengazo.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kwakuthe cwaka ngexesha uBharnabha noPawulos besenza ingxelo ngemimangaliso nemiqondiso ayenzileyo uThixo ngabo phakathi kweentlanga.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Emva kwentetho yabo kwathetha uYakobi, wathi: “Ndiphulaphuleni, mawethu!",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> USimon unichazele indlela uThixo abonakalise ngayo ukuzikhathalela kwakhe iintlanga ngokukhetha phakathi kwazo abantu abangabakhe.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Amazwi *abashumayeli ayavumelana nesi senzo, kuba zithi *iziBhalo:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “ ‘Emva koku ndiya kubuya,’ itsho iNkosi, ‘ndiwuvuse umzi kaDavide ongamanxiwa, ndiwulungise apho wonakele khona, ume kakuhle.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bothi ke bayifune iNkosi bonke abantu, zonke izizwe endizibizileyo zaba zezam,’ itsho iNkosi, yona ikwenzileyo oku.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Kakade ke iyaziwa le nto.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ke ngoko mna ndithi masingazixhamli iintlanga eziguqukayo,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> koko masizibhalele incwadi sizixelele ukuba mazingatyi naluphi na uhlobo lokutya okungahlambulukanga ngenxa yokubingelelwa kwizithixo, zizigcine nyulu ekurheletyeni, zingatyi nasiphi na isilo esikrwitshiweyo, nanyama inegazi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Sekukudala kakade ufundwa umthetho kaMosis, kushunyayelwa amazwi akhe ngayo yonke *iMihla yokuPhumla *ezindlwini zesikhungo kwiidolophu ngeedolophu.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> *Abathunywa nabadala, kunye nebandla lonke, bafika kwisigqibo sokuba kukhethwe amadoda phakathi kwabo, athunywe eAntiyokwe kunye noPawulos noBharnabha. Banyulwa ke ooJudas ogama limbi linguBharsabha kunye noSilas, ingamadoda awayebekwe kakhulu ngamakholwa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Banikwa incwadi ukuba bahambe nayo. Ke yona yayibhalwe ngolu hlobo: “Thina bathunywa sikunye nabadala siyanibulisa njengamawethu xa ninonke, nina zizwe zaseAntiyokwe eSiriya naseKiliki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Sivile ukuba kubekho madoda athile aphuma apha kuthi aza kunixhamla, eniphazamisa ngento esingawathumanga yona, ayithethileyo kuni.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Sihlangene ke, savumelana sonke ukuba sinyule izigidimi sizithume kuni, zihambe kunye nabahlobo bethu abaziintanda, uBharnabha noPawulos,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> amadoda ancame ubomi bawo ngenxa yokukhonza uKrestu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ke ngoko sinithumela uJudas noSilas abaya kunichazela ngokwabo ezi zinto kanye sizibhalileyo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Thina samkele isigqibo soMoya oyiNgcwele sokuba singanithwalisi bunzima bumbi ngaphandle kwale migaqo ibalulekileyo:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Musani ukuyitya into ebingelelwe kwizithixo, nenyama enegazi, nesilo esikrwitshiweyo; nizigcine nyulu ekurheletyeni. Niya kuba niyakholisa xa nizilumlayo kwezo zinto. Salani kakuhle.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Izigidimi ezo zandululwa, zasinga eAntiyokwe, apho zafika zawahlanganisa amakholwa, zawanika incwadi leyo.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bathi abantu bakuyifunda incwadi leyo, bavuya kakhulu ziindaba zayo zenkuthazo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> UJudas noSilas, ababengabashumayeli ngokwabo, bathetha ixesha elide namakholwa, bewakhuthaza, bewomeleza.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Emva kwexesha belapho bakhululwa ngoxolo ngamakholwa, baza bagoduka. [",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kodwa uSilas yena wabona ukuba makasale khona.]",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> UPawulos noBharnabha bona bakhe banexesha belapho eAntiyokwe. Bekunye nabanye balifundisa, balishumayela, ilizwi leNkosi.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ekuhambeni kwexesha wathi uPawulos kuBharnabha: “Makhe sityelele amakholwa kuzo zonke iidolophu apho sasikhe salishumayela khona ilizwi leNkosi, siqonde ukuba aphila njani na.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> UBharnabha wafuna ukuba kuhanjwe noYohane Marko,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> kodwa uPawulos yena akathandanga ukuba bahambe naye, kuba ngokuya babehambe naye kuqala wajika esithubeni, wabashiya ePamfili.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Baxambulisana ke ngale ndawo, bada bagqibela ngokwahlukana. UBharnabha wahamba noMarko, basinga eSipro ngesikhephe.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Waza yena uPawulos wakhetha ukuhamba noSilas. Ke amakholwa abanikela ezibeleni zikaThixo, bemka.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> UPawulos watyhutyha imimandla yaseSiriya naseKiliki, ewomeleza amabandla."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> UPawulos waya eDerbhe naseListra. Apho kwakukho ikholwa eligama linguTimoti, onina wayekwalikholwa, engumJudakazi, uyise yena engumGrike.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onke amakholwa aseListra naseIkoniyo ayemazi ngesimilo esihle uTimoti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> UPawulos wafuna ukuhamba noTimoti, ngoko ke wamolùsa kuqala, kuba onke amaJuda aloo mmandla ayesazi ukuba uyise wayengolukanga.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ekuzityhutyheni kwabo ezo dolophu, amakholwa bawazisa ngesigqibo *sabathunywa nabadala eJerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Aza ke amabandla omelezeka elukholweni, anda nangamanani imihla ngemihla.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Xa babekwingingqi yaseFrigi naseGalati, uMoya oyiNgcwele wabalela ukuba balishumayele ilizwi eAsiya.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bakufika emdeni waseMisi, bazama ukungena eBhitini, kodwa nakhona uMoya kaYesu akabavumelanga.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngoko ke bacanda eMisi, behla baya eTrowa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Xa babelapho ke, ebusuku uPawulos wabona umbono. Indoda yaseMakedoni yayimile imcenga isithi: “Yiza apha eMakedoni, uzokusinceda.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngokukhawuleza emva kwalo mbono kaPawulos, salungiselela ukuya eMakedoni, kuba saqonda ukuba uThixo usibizela ukuba siye kuzishumayela iindaba ezimnandi kubantu balapho.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Semka ngesikhephe eTrowa, sahamba ngqo sacanda sijonge eSamotraki, saza ngengomso sangena eNapoli.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Sakusuka apho, saya kutsho eFilipi, idolophu yokuqala kwisithili saseMakedoni, eyayilithânga laseRoma. Sakhe sahlala iintsukwana apho kuloo dolophu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> *NgoMhla wokuPhumla saphuma edolophini, saya ngasemlanjeni, apho sasiba koba kukho indawo athandazela kuyo amaJuda. Sahlala phantsi, sancokola namakhosikazi awayebuthe apho.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Enye yawo eyayisiphulaphule nguLidiya waseTiyatire, owayengumthengisi weempahla ezimsobo zexabiso. Wayeyintokazi eyayimhlonela uThixo, yaza ke iNkosi yayibaza ingqondo ukuba izigqale izinto ezazithethwa nguPawulos.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Yabhaptizwa kunye nosapho lwayo. Yaza ke yasimema isithi: “Ukuba nithi ndilikholwa ngenene eNkosini, khanizokuhlala kwam.” Yasithundeza ke ukuba siye.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngamhla uthile xa sasisiya kwindawo yokuthandaza, sahlangana nentombi eyayilikhoboka. Yayinamafufunyana. Yayibenzela imali eninzi ke abanikaziyo ngokuchazela abantu izinto eziza kubehlela.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Yasilandela sinoPawulos, ikhwaza isithi: “La madoda angabakhonzi bakaThixo uPhezukonke. Anishumayeza indlela eningásindiswa ngayo.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Yaqhuba iintsuku ezininzi iyenza le nto, yada yamthukuthezela uPawulos, wajika wathi kuloo moya: “Ngengunya legama likaYesu Krestu ndithi: ‘Phuma kule ntombi.’ ” Aphuma kwangoko amafufunyana.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bakuphawula abanikaziyo ukuba ayisekho indlela yokwenza imali ngale ntombi, babagxavula ooPawulos noSilas, babarhuqela kwinkundla yamatyala eyayisebaleni lembutho.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Babamangalela kwabasemagunyeni, besithi: “La madoda angamaJuda, yaye adala isidubedube apha edolophini yethu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Afundisa imikhwa enxamnye nomthetho wethu. Thina singamaRoma, asinakuyamkela loo mikhwa.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nesihlwele sangenelela ekubahlaseleni. Zaza iziphathamandla zathi mazikrazulwe izambatho zikaPawulos noSilas, babethwe nokubethwa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bakuba bebethwe kanobom, bavalelwa entolongweni. Wayalelwa nojela ukuba abatshixele abagcine ngokunqabileyo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ewufumene umyalelo lowo, ujela wabatshixela kwelingaphakathi igumbi, wabakhonkxa iinyawo ngezikhuni.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Phakathi kobusuku uPawulos noSilas bathandaza bacula bedumisa uThixo, namanye amabanjwa ebeva.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngesaquphe kwabakho inyikima eyashukumisa izisekelo zentolongo. Zatsho zavuleka zonke iingcango, namatyathanga akhululeka kumabanjwa.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Evukile ujela, wabona iingcango zentolongo zivulekile, wacinga ukuba abalekile amabanjwa onke; waza warhola ikrele lakhe, eza kuzibulala.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kuthe kusenjalo wamemeza uPawulos esithi: “Mus' ukuzenzakalisa, kuba sisaphelele!”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ujela lowo wathi makuziwe nesibane, waza engcangcazela enjalo wangena wawa ezinyaweni zikaPawulos noSilas.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Wabakhuphela phandle, wabuza wathi: “Bahlekazi, ndingenza ntoni ukuze ndisinde?” Bona baphendula bathi:",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Zinikele eNkosini uYesu; uya kusindiswa wena nosapho lwakho.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bamchazela ke yena nabo bonke ababesendlwini yakhe ngodaba lweNkosi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ngaloo yure kanye yobusuku ujela wabathatha, wahlamba amanxeba abo; waza wabhaptizwa kunye nosapho lwakhe kwangoko.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Waya nabo endlwini yakhe ooPawulos noSilas, wabapha ukutya. Yena nosapho lwakhe bazaliswa luvuyo ngenxa yokuba bezinikele kuThixo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ngentsasa elandelayo abasemagunyeni bathumela amagosa abo, besithi: “Wakhululeni loo madoda.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ujela ke wamxelela uPawulos ukuba iziphathamandla zithumele umyalelo wokuba yena noSilas bangákhululwa. Ngoko ke bakhululekile bangáhamba ngoxolo.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kodwa waphendula uPawulos wathi kumagosa lawo: “Hayi kaloku, sikatswe esidlangalaleni, nakuba singakhange sibekwe tyala, ibe futhi singabemi abangamaRoma! Ngaphezu koko sivalelwe entolongweni. Bangathini ke ngoku ukusikhulula bucala? Hayi bo! Ayinakwenzeka loo nto! Abasemagunyeni mabeze kusikhulula ngokwabo.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Amagosa lawo aya kuwaxela la mazwi kwiziphathamandla, ezathi zakuva ukuba uPawulos noSilas ngabemi abangamaRoma, zoyika kakhulu.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ngoko ke zaya kubo, zacela uxolo, zabacenga ukuba bahambe, zabakhupha ke bemka.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> UPawulos noSilas bayishiya ke intolongo leyo, baya kwaLidiya. Apho ke bahlangana namakholwa, baza bathi, bakuba bewakhuthazile, bemka."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bahamba ke, badlula eAmfipoli naseApoloniya, bada baya kufika eTesalonika, apho yayikho *indlu yesikhungo yamaJuda.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Njengoko ebeqhele ukwenjenjalo, uPawulos waya endlwini yesikhungo leyo. Apho wayexoxa nabantu *ngeziBhalo imiGqibelo emithathu,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ezichaza iziBhalo, ecacisa kwangazo ukuba ubemelwe kukuva ubunzima *uKrestu, abuye avuke ekufeni. “Lo Yesu ndimvakalisayo nguKrestu,” wayesitsho uPawulos.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Abanye abantu boyisakala, bazimanya noPawulos noSilas. Enjenjalo namaGrike aliqela awayemhlonela uThixo, kwakunye namakhosikazi amaninzi aphambili entlalweni.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kodwa akhathazeka amaJuda, aqokelela amatshijolo ezitalatweni, yaligquba elenza intswahla nesiphithi-phithi edolophini. Lawuhlasela umzi kaJason, liba balapho ooPawulos noSilas, liza kubasa ematyaleni.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kodwa lakungabafumani, larhuqa uJason kunye namanye amakholwa, libasa kubaphathi-dolophu, likhwaza lisithi: “La madoda luqhushululu konke apho ahamba khona; ngoku eze nakule idolophu,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> yaye uJason uwagcine phaya endlwini yakhe. Ewonke angabaphuli-mthetho *kaKhesare, kuba athi kukho nkosi yimbi inguKrestu Yesu.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngaloo mazwi basitsho isihlwele nabaphathi-dolophu bakhathazeka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Abaphathi-dolophu babahlawulisa imali yesibambiso ooJason nabanye abo ngaphambi kokubakhulula bahambe.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kuthe nje kusandul' ukuhlwa, amakholwa abathumela eBheriya ooPawulos noSilas. Bafika apho, baya *kwindlu yesikhungo yamaJuda.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Abantu balapho bona babeneengqondo eziphangaleleyo kunabantu baseTesalonika. Baluphulaphula ngomdla bona udaba, bazifunda mihla le *neziBhalo, befuna ukuqonda ukuba uPawulos unyanisile na.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kwaguquka abantu abaninzi, amadoda kunye namakhosikazi amaGrike akumgangatho ophezulu entlalweni.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kodwa akuva amaJuda aseTesalonika ukuba uPawulos ulishumayela naseBheriya ilizwi likaThixo, aya apho, afika afaka umoya woqhushululu ebantwini.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Amakholwa amsa ngaselwandle uPawulos kwangoko. Basala bona ooSilas noTimoti eBheriya.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> La madoda âhamba noPawulos, ada aya kutsho eAtene. Abuyela eBheriya nomyalelo kaPawulos wokuba ooSilas noTimoti mabakhawuleze baye kuye.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kwathi xa uPawulos wayesalinde uSilas noTimoti eAtene, wafumana umnqa kukubona indlela ezazizininzi ngayo izithixo kuloo dolophu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Waxoxa endlwini yesikhungo namaJuda kunye neentlanga ezazihlonela uThixo. Ngokukwanjalo wayexoxa nabantu ababegqitha-gqitha ebaleni lembutho.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nabathile abaziintanda-bulumko zeqela *lamaEpikure *namaStoyike babencokola naye. Bambi babesithi: “Ngaba lifuna ukuthini eli pholopholo?” abanye besithi: “Ngathi ngunozakuzaku *woothixo basemzini.” Babesitsho ke kuba uPawulos wayeshumayela ngoYesu nangovuko lwabafileyo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Baza ke bamthatha uPawulos, baya naye entlanganisweni, endaweni ekwakusithiwa yiAriyopago, bathi kuye: “Khawutsho! Sifuna ukuyazi le mfundiso intsha uthetha ngayo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ezinye zezinto esikuva uthetha ngazo ziyasimangalisa, ngoko ke sifuna ukuyazi intsingiselo yazo.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kaloku abantu baseAtene nabatyeleli bakhona kwakungekho nto babeyixabise ngaphezu kokuncokola okanye ukuphulaphula iingcamango ezintsha.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> UPawulos waphakama wema entlanganisweni apho eAriyopago, wathi: “Bantu baseAtene, ndiyaphawula ukuba ningabantu abaluthanda ngokuncamisayo unqulo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kuthe xa bendihamba-hamba ndibuka iindawo zenu zonqulo, ndabona neqonga lamadini elibhaliweyo kwathiwa: ‘Kongaziwayo uThixo.’ Ngoko ke lowo nina nimnqula ningamazi, mna ndivakalisa yena kuni.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> UThixo lo udale ihlabathi nezinto ezikulo, uyiNkosi yezulu nomhlaba. Ngoko ke akahlali zindlwini zenziwe ngabantu,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> engaswele nto ngokokude abantu bazidube ngokumenzela nto. Kuba kaloku nguye ngokwakhe onika ubomi nomphefumlo, nazo zonke iimfuneko zoluntu lonke.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Zonke iintlanga zabantu wazidala zaphuma mlibeni mnye, wazenza ukuba ziwume wonke umhlaba. Yena ngokwakhe kwangaphambili wazimisela amaxesha obomi, kunye nemida yokuhlala kwazo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Oku wakwenza ukuze zihlale zimzingela, hleze zimphuthaphuthe de zimfumane; nangona yena uThixo engekude kuthi sonke,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> kuba kungaye sikho nje, sisuka-suka, siphilile. Kunjengoko zitshoyo ezinye zeembongi zenu ukuthi: ‘Nathi siyinzala yakhe.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Singabantwana bakhe nje ke, masingacingi ukuba imo kaThixo ifana nento eqingqwe ngegolide, ngesiliva, okanye ngelitye, ngobugcisa bomntu.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> UThixo wayewayeke ngabom loo maxesha apho abantu babengazi. Kungokunje uyalela abantu bonke, ezindaweni zonke, ukuba baguquke ezindleleni zabo ezimbi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kaloku uwumisele umhla apho aya kuligweba ihlabathi lonke liphela ngobulungisa, ngeNdoda ayimiseleyo. Le nto uyingqine kubantu bonke ngokuyivusa loo Ndoda ekufeni.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bathi bakumva uPawulos ethetha ngovuko lwabafileyo, bahlekisa ngaye. Bambi bathi: “Sisafuna ukuyiva kwakhona le ntetho yakho.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Waza ke uPawulos wemka apho entlanganisweni.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kambe abanye bazinikela, baza bamlandela. Phakathi kwabo kwakukho uDiyonisi, ilungu leAriyopago, nomfazi ogama linguDamari, kunye nabanye."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Emva koko uPawulos wemka eAtene, wabheka eKorinte.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Apho wadibana nomJuda ogama linguAkwila, owazalelwa ePonto, ekunye noPrisila umkakhe. Wayesand' ukufika apho, evela eItali, ekubeni *uKhesare Klawudiyo wawagxothayo amaJuda awayeseRoma. Ebandwendwele uPawulos,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> wahlala kunye nabo, wasebenza kunye nabo, kuba kaloku wayephila ngokwenza iintente njengabo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Yonke imiGqibelo wayedla ngokubamba iingxoxo *endlwini yesikhungo, ezama ukuwanelisa amaJuda kwanamaGrike.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bakufika ooSilas noTimoti, bevela eMakedoni, uPawulos akabanga senza nto yimbi ingekuko ukushumayela iindaba ezimnandi, ewacacisela amaJuda ukuba uYesu unguye uKrestu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kuthe akumchasa emngcikiva, wavuthulula iimpahla zakhe, ekhalala, esithi: “Ukuba nithe natshabalala, lityala lenu. Mna andinatyala kuloo nto. Ukususela ngoku ndiya ezintlangeni.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Wabashiya ke waya kuhlala emzini kaTitiyo Yusto intlanga eyayimnqula uThixo. Umzi wakhe wawumelene nendlu yesikhungo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UKrispo, igosa lendlu yesikhungo, wazinikela eNkosini kunye nentsapho yakhe. Kwabhaptizwa nenkitha yabantu eKorinte eyalivayo ilizwi yazinikela eNkosini.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngabusuku buthile uPawulos waba nombono apho, yathi iNkosi kuye: “Sukoyika, zingisa ukuthetha ungancami,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> kuba mna ndinawe. Akukho mntu uya kukuchukumisa, kuba baninzi abantu bam kule dolophu.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> UPawulos wahlala apho ke unyaka onesiqingatha, ebafundisa ilizwi likaThixo abantu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kwathi akuba uGaliyo eyirhuluneli emele amaRoma kwisithili saseAkaya, amaJuda adibana ngoPawulos, amthatha amsa enkundleni, afika athi:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Le ndoda izama ukuwexula abantu ukuba bakhonze uThixo ngendlela ephambeneyo nomthetho.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kwathi xa aza kuphendula uPawulos, uGaliyo wabhekisa kumaJuda wathi: “Ukuba ngaba lo mbandela ubuyimpazamo ethile, okanye ityala elibi, bendingade ndiyinyamezele le nto, maJuda.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kodwa ke ngenxa yokuba lo mbandela uphathelele kumazwi, namagama, nomthetho wenu, ziboneleni nina ukuba ningawulungisa njani na. Mna andinakugweba izinto ezinjalo.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Waza ke wabakhupha apho enkundleni.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bahlasela uSosteno igosa lendlu yesikhungo, bambethela apho phambi kwenkundla. Kodwa yena uGaliyo zange azikhathaze ngaloo nto.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> UPawulos wahlala apho eKorinte ixesha elide, waza ke wanduluka apho ngesikhephe enoPrisila noAkwila, basinga eSiriya. Wathi xa aseKenkreya wacheba intloko yakhe, kuba wayenze isifungo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bakufika e-Efese, uPawulos wabashiya ooPrisila noAkwila, waya endlwini yesikhungo, waxoxa khona namaJuda.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Babemcela ukuba ahlale nabo ixesha elide, kodwa akavuma.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Wasuka wathi xa ahambayo: “Ukuba ngaba kuyintando kaThixo ukuba ndibuye, ndobuya ndibuye.” Waza ke wemka e-Efese.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Akufika eKhesariya, wadlula waya kubulisa ibandla, waza ke waya eAntiyokwe.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Emva kwethuba elapho wemka, watyhutyha imimandla yaseGalati neyaseFrigi, ehamba ewomeleza onke amakholwa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> E-Efese kwafika umJuda, ogama linguApolo, owazalelwa eAlesandriya. Wayeliciko lokuthetha, futhi ezazi ngokucokisekileyo *iziBhalo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Wayeqeqeshiwe ngeNdlela yeNkosi, ngokunjalo wayethetha ngokutshiseka ezifundisa iinyaniso ezingoYesu ngentembeko. Nangona kunjalo wayesazi ubhaptizo lukaYohane kuphela.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Wayethetha ngesibindi *endlwini yesikhungo. Bathi ke bakumva ooPrisila noAkwila, bammemela emzini wabo, bamcacisela kakuhle ngokuzeleyo iNdlela yeNkosi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> UApolo wagqiba ukuba aye kwelaseAkaya, aza amakholwa ase-Efese amkhuthaza amphathisa neleta emazisayo kumakholwa alapho. Akufika khona waba luncedo olukhulu kwabo babethe ngesisa sikaThixo baguquka,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> kuba ngenxa yobuciko bakhe wayewoyisa amaJuda ezingxoxweni. Kaloku wayecaphula eziBhalweni, ebonisa ukuba uYesu *unguKrestu."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngexesha uApolo wayeseKorinte, uPawulos yena wacanda phakathi kuloo mimandla, waya kufika e-Efese. Apho wafumana iqela labalandeli bakaYohane,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> wababuza wathi: “Namamkela na uMoya oyiNgcwele ukuzinikela kwenu?” Baphendula bathi: “Asizange sive nokuva ukuba kukho uMoya oyiNgcwele.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> UPawulos wababuza wathi: “Phofu lubhaptizo luni enabhaptizwa ngalo?” Bona bathi: “Lubhaptizo lukaYohane.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> UPawulos wabachazela wathi: “Ubhaptizo lukaYohane lona lwalusalatha inguquko. Yena wayebaxelela abantu ukuba bazinikele kulowo wayesiza emva kwakhe; nguYesu ke lowo.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bakuyiva le ntetho, babhaptizwa egameni leNkosi uYesu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> UPawulos wababeka izandla, batsho bamamkela uMoya oyiNgcwele, baza bathetha iilwimi, belithetha ilizwi likaThixo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Babengamadoda amalunga neshumi elinambini.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngesithuba seenyanga ezintathu uPawulos wayesiya *endlwini yesikhungo yamaJuda, ethetha, exoxa nabo abantu ngesibindi, ezama ukuboyisela ekulawulweni nguThixo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kodwa abanye babo baba neenkani, abavuma ukuzinikela, basuka bayingcikiva iNdlela yeNkosi esidlangalaleni. Ngoko ke uPawulos wabashiya, wathatha abalandeli bakaYesu, waza wafundisa imihla ngemihla esikolweni sikaTirano.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Le nto ke wayiqhuba isithuba seminyaka emibini, bada bonke abantu ababehlala kwelo phondo laseAsiya, amaJuda kwanamaGrike, baliva ilizwi leNkosi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Amandla kaThixo âbonakala ngezinto ezingaqhelekanga ezazisenziwa nguPawulos.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Neetshefu ezi kwaneefaskoti ezichukumise umzimba kaPawulos zazibaphilisa abagulayo, kude kuphume neendimoni.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> AmaJuda athile awayejikeleza ekhupha iindimoni, nawo akhe azama ukusebenzisa igama leNkosi uYesu. Ayesithi kwiindimoni: “Ndikuyala ngegama likaYesu, lo ushunyayelwa nguPawulos.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Aba babesenza le nto yayingoonyana abasixhenxe bombingeleli oyintloko womJuda owayenguSkeva igama.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kodwa indimoni yathi kubo: “Ndiyamazi uYesu, noPawulos ndiyamazi; nina ke ningoobani?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ke kaloku indoda leyo yayinendimoni yabahlasela yabongamela, ibadlakazelisa kangangokuba baphuma apho kuloo ndlu bagqotsa bengxwelerhekile, neempahla zabo zivukuvuku.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Onke amaJuda neentlanga ezazihlala apho e-Efese zasiva esi siganeko, zaza zoyika kakhulu; laza igama leNkosi uYesu lanikwa imbeko ladunyiswa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Amakholwa amaninzi azinikezela, ezivuma ezixela esidlangalaleni izinto azenzileyo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Uninzi lwâbo babesenza imilingo lwaziqokelela lwazitshisela esidlangalaleni iincwadi zalo. Bawabala bawadibanisa amaxabiso ezo ncwadi, bazifumana zikwisithuba samashumi amahlanu amawaka eerandi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ngamandla eNkosi ilizwi leNkosi lanwenwezela, lakhula, laya lisomelela ngokomelela ngale ndlela.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Emva koko uPawulos wazimisela ukucanda kwelaseMakedoni nelaseAkaya, aze agqithele eJerusalem. “Ndakuba ndiyile khona, kufuneka ndiyibone neRoma,” wakha watsho.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ke kaloku wathumela eMakedoni uTimoti noErasto abancedisi bakhe, lo gama athe yena wolula ukuhlala kwiphondo laseAsiya.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kungeli xesha ke apho kwavumbuluka udushe e-Efese ngenxa yeNdlela yeNkosi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> UDemetriyo umfo owayebumba imifanekiso yendlu yesithixokazi *uArtemis ngesiliva, wayewenzela ingeniso enkulu ngolu shishino amagcisa aqeshwe nguye.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Wenza imbizo ke ekwabakho kuyo abaqeshwa kwakunye nabanye ababesenza umsebenzi okwanjengowakhe, wathi kubo: “Madoda, niyazi ukuba impumelelo yethu ixhomekeke kolu shishino.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Niyabona nizivela ngokwenu into eyenziwa yile nkewu uPawulos. Uthi *oothixo abenziwe ngabantu àbangabo konke, yaye uphumelele ekuboyiseni abantu abaninzi jikelele kule Efese, phantse wawugqiba ummandla waseAsiya uphela.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ilapha ke ingozi, kule ndawo yokuba ushishino olu lwethu lufumane igama elibi. Kanti asikokuphela kwaloo nto, ikwakho nale ndawo yokuba nendlu yesithixokazi uArtemis ayiyi kwazelwa nto, ukanti nesidima sesithixokazi saseAsiya – nditsho esinqulwa lihlabathi liphela – siya kuphanza.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Iwaphulaphule la mazwi indimbane leyo, yakhathazeka kakhulu, yadanduluka yathi: “Mkhulu uArtemis wamaEfese!”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Le ntshukumo yatyhutyha yonke idolophu. Bahlasela uGayo noAristarko baseMakedoni ababehamba kunye noPawulos, babaqweqwedisela kwiqonga lemidlalo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> UPawulos wafuna ukungena phakathi kwesihlwele eso, ukuze athethe naso, kodwa amakholwa akamvumelanga.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Abathile kumagosa ephondo laseAsiya, ababenobuhlobo noPawulos, nabo bamthumela umyalezo, bemcebisa ukuba angayi phaya eqongeni lemidlalo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kwangeli xesha ke intlanganiso xa iyonke yayisisiphithi-phithi nje. Kaloku abanye babekhwaza bethetha le, bambi bekhwaza bethetha leya; kuba kaloku uninzi lwaluhamba nje nezihlwele, lungazi nokuba indibano le yeyantoni na.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Abanye abantu bamchazela ngale nto yenzekayo uAlesandire, kuba amaJuda ayegqatse yena phambili. UAlesandire wawangawangisa ngesandla ukuba kuthi cwaka, efuna ukulamla.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kodwa bathi bakumqonda ukuba ungumJuda, batsho ngazwinye, besenza intswahla, bekhwaza, bephinda-phinda besithi: “Mkhulu uArtemis wamaEfese!” Kwada kwaphela iiyure ezimbini besenza loo nto.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kwathi ngelikade unobhala wedolophu wada wanako ukusithomalalisa isihlwele. Wathi: “MaEfese, wonke ubani uyazi ukuba le dolophu yase-Efese ngumgcini wendlu yesikhulukazi uArtemis, nowomfanekiso oqingqiweyo owavela ezulwini.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Akukho bani unako ukuziphikisa ezi zinto. Ngoko ke zolani, ningenzi nto ngokungakhathali.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> La madoda nize nawo apha, nangona angebanga zinto zingcwele zendlu yonqulo okanye anyelise isithixokazi sethu.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ukuba uDemetriyo nezicaka zakhe banesityholo ngakubani, ikho imihla eyaziwayo yenkundla, neziphathamandla zikhona; bangamangalelana khona.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Kodwa ukuba kukho enye into, inokulungiswa yintlanganiso esemthethweni yabemi.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kaloku ngenxa yale nto yehle namhlanje, sisengozini yokutyholwa ngokwenza ingxushungxushu. Asinandlela yakuziphendulela ngolu dushe, singenaso nesizathu esibambekayo.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Akuba etshilo, wayichitha intlanganiso."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Lwakuba ludambile udushe olo, uPawulos wawahlanganisa amakholwa, wawanika amazwi enkuthazo nawokwahlukana. Waza wasuka apho wasinga kwelaseMakedoni.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Watyhutyha loo mimandla, ehamba ethetha amazwi enkuthazo ebantwini. Wafika nakwelamaGrike,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> apho wahlala iinyanga ezintathu. Wathi xa alungiselela ukuya eSiriya, wabhaqa ukuba amaJuda amenzela iyelenqe, waza wabona ukuba makaphindele emva, acande kwelaseMakedoni.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nâba abâmkhapháyo: uSopatro unyana kaPiro waseBheriya, uAristarko noSekundo baseTesalonika, uGayo waseDerbhe noTimoti, kwanoTikiko noTrofimo baseAsiya.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Basandulela baya kusilinda eTrowa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Emva *kweSidlo seZonka ezingenaGwele sanduluka eFilipi ngesikhephe, saza emva kweentsuku ezintlanu sadibana nabo eTrowa, apho sachitha iveki khona.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngokuhlwa koMgqibelo sahlanganisana kwisidlo sobudlelwana. UPawulos wathetha nabo abantu, wolula kwada kwaphakathi kobusuku, kuba kaloku wayeza kuhamba ngomhla olandelayo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Intlanganiso leyo yayisegumbini eliphezulu apho kwakukho izibane ezininzi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Umfana ogama linguYutiko wayehleli efestileni, wada wozela walala, kuba uPawulos engayeki ukuthetha. Wothuleka apho kumngangatho wesithathu, waya kuwa emhlabeni, bamchola apho efile.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> UPawulos wehla waya kuye, wafika waziphosa phezu kwakhe, wamgona, wathi: “Sanukothuka, kuba akafanga, uhleli!”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Waza ke uPawulos wenyuka waya egumbini eliphezulu, wafika wathatha isonka watya. UPawulos wathetha nabo kwada kwaphuma ilanga, waza ke wemka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Umfana lowo bagoduka naye ephilile, nabo bethuthuzelekile.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Thina sahlabela mgama, sihamba ngenqanawa, saya kutsho eAso, apho sasiza kuthatha uPawulos khona, kuba lo yayingumyalelo wakhe, njengoko yena wayehamba emhlabeni.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Wathi akudibana nathi eAso, sahamba naye saya kufika eMitilene.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sasuka apho, saya kudlula malunga neKiyo ngosuku olulandelayo. Kwakhona ngemini elandelayo safika eSamo, saza ngengomso saya kufika eMileto.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> UPawulos wayegqibe ukuba angagqithi e-Efese, ukuze angachithi xesha kwiphondo laseAsiya. Wayengxamele ukuba usuku *lwePentekoste lumfikele eseJerusalem xa kunokwenzeka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Sathi xa siseMileto, uPawulos wathumela e-Efese, ukuba abadala bebandla baye kuye.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bakufika wathi kubo: “Nina ngokwenu niyayazi kakuhle indlela endahlala nani ngayo, ukusuka kwimini yokuqala endathi ndafika ngayo kweli phondo laseAsiya.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Njengesicaka seNkosi, umsebenzi wam ndawenza ngentobeko ndisezinyembezini, nakumaxesha anzima ândifikeláyo ngenxa yamayelenqe amaJuda.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Niyazi ukuba andinifihlelanga nto ebinokuba luncedo kuni, xa bendishumayela ndinifundisa esidlangalaleni nasemakhayeni enu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> KumaJuda nasezintlangeni ndazingisa ukubalumkisa abantu ukuba baguqukele kuThixo beyivuma iNkosi yethu uYesu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ngoku ke ngokuthundezwa nguMoya oyiNgcwele ndiya eJerusalem, ndingayazi into eya kundihlela khona.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ndazi nto-nye, le yokuba kuzo zonke iidolophu uMoya oyiNgcwele undilumkisile ukuba ndilindelwe yintolongo neenkxwaleko.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kodwa kum ukuphila akubalulekanga ngaphezu kokuba ndilufeze ubizo lwam, ndiwugqibe umsebenzi endawunikwa yiNkosi wokuvakalisa iindaba ezimnandi zesisa sikaThixo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Ndijikelezile phakathi kwenu, ndivakalisa ngolawulo lukaThixo kuni. Ibe ngoku ndazi kakuhle ukuba akukho bani kuni uya kuphinda andibone.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngokunjalo ndingqina ndiqinisekile ngayo le mini ukuba xa kuthe kwakho umntu olahlekayo apha kuni, ndimsulwa mna,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> kuba andizange ndifihle nto – ndalivakalisa njengoko linjalo icebo likaThixo kuni.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Zilumkeleni nina ngokwenu, niwulumkele nawo umhlambi athe uMoya oyiNgcwele wanibeka phezu kwawo. Yibani ngabelúsi bebandla likaThixo, athe walizuza ngegazi lowakhe uNyana.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kuba ndiyazi ukuba ndakumka, kuya kuvela kwalapha kuni iingcuka eziqwengayo, ezingayi kuba nanceba ngomhlambi lo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kwalapha kuni kuya kubakho amadoda agqwetha inyaniso, enenjongo yokuwalahlekisa amakholwa.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Lumkani ngoko, nikhumbule ukuba imini nobusuku ndaniluleka nonke ngabanye, ndisezinyembezini, ithuba leminyaka emithathu.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Ngoko ke ndiyambongoza uThixo ukuba makanikhusele. Uya kunakha ngodaba lwesisa sakhe, olunamandla okunenza nilixhamle ilifa kunye nabo bonke abantu bakhe.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Andizange ndinqwenele mali nampahla yamntu.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kaloku nazi mhlophe ukuba ndasebenza ngezi zandla zam, ndizixhasa kuzo zonke iintswelo zam kwanezamahlakani am.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ndinibonisile ngeendlela zonke ukuba sifanele ukusebenza nzima, ukuze sincede nabo bahluphekileyo, siwakhumbula amazwi eNkosi athi: ‘Kuluyolo ukupha ngaphezu kokuphiwa.’ ”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Akuwagqiba la mazwi uPawulos, waguqa nabo bonke, wathandaza.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bathi besithi ndlela-ntle kuye, baye bengenakuzibamba bengqukruleka. Babemgona ngokwesiko labo.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Babehlatyaniselwe ngokukodwa ngamazwi awawathetháyo esithi abayi kuphinda bambone. Baza ke bamkhapha, baya naye enqanaweni."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Sakwahlukana nabo, sangena enqanaweni, sahamba ngqo sada saya kufika eKos. Ngengomso sagaleleka eRodo, sasuka saya kutsho ePatara.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Safumana inqanawa apho eyayisiya eFenike, saza sangena kuyo, sahamba ngayo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sayithi ntlaa, sayishiya ngasekhohlo iSipro, sijonge eSiriya. Sehla enqanaweni eTire. Kaloku kwakulapho yayiza kothulwa khona umthwalo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Safika kukho amakholwa apho, saya kuhlala nawo iveki yonke. Ngokutyhilelwa nguMoya oyiNgcwele athi uPawulos makangayi eJerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kodwa lakufika ixesha lokumka, sayihamba indlela yethu. Basikhapha sada sangaphandle kwedolophu, bekunye nabafazi kwanabantwana babo. Saguqa elunxwemeni apho, sathandaza.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sahlukana ke, thina sangena enqanaweni, bona bagoduka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ukusuka kwethu eTire, sahamba sada saya kufika eTolimayi. Apho sadibana namakholwa, sahlala nawo imini yonke.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kwakusa salishiya elo, saya kungena eKhesariya. Apho safikela emzini womvakalisi weendaba ezimnandi uFilipu, omnye walaa madoda asixhenxe awanyulwa eJerusalem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wayeneentombi ezine ezingendanga ezaziluvakalisa udaba lweNkosi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kuthe sekuntsuku silapho, kwafika umvakalisi-daba onguAgabho, evela kwaJuda.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ufike wathatha ibhanti kaPawulos, wazibopha ngayo iinyawo nezandla, wathi: “Uthi uMoya oyiNgcwele: ‘Umnini wale bhanti uya kubotshwa enjiwenje ngamaJuda eJerusalem, yaye aya kumnikela ezintlangeni.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Sakuyiva le nto, samcenga uPawulos, sikunye namakholwa alapho, ukuba angayi eJerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kodwa wathi ukuphendula: “Nenza ntoni, nifuna ukundityhafisa nje ngezi nyembezi zenu? Andilungelanga kubotshwa kuphela eJerusalem; kwanokufa oku ndikulungele ngenxa yeNkosi uYesu.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Sancama ke, kuba singabanga nakumoyisa, sathi: “Makwenzeke ukuthanda kweNkosi.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Emva kwexesha silapho salungiselela ukuya eJerusalem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Abanye babalandeli bakaYesu baseKhesariya bahamba nathi, basisa endlwini yendoda egama linguMnaso, esathi sahlala nayo. Loo ndoda yayingumfo waseSipro, ilikholwa elaguquka kwimihla yangaphambili.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ekufikeni kwethu eJerusalem, amakholwa asamkela ngezandla ezishushu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ngengomso sahamba noPawulos, saya kubona uYakobi. Nabo bonke abadala bebandla babekhona.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ebabulisile uPawulos, wabanika ingxelo epheleleyo ngezinto zonke uThixo awayezenzile ngaye phakathi kweentlanga.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bathi bakuziva, bamdumisa uThixo xa bebonke. Baza bacebisa bathi kuPawulos: “Mfondini, nawe uyazibonela ngokwakho ukuba apha kukho amawaka-waka amaJuda aguqukileyo angamakholwa, kodwa asabambelele *emthethweni kaMosis.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Evile ke ngawe ukuba wena ufundisa onke amaJuda ahlala kumazwe eentlanga, ukuba awulahle umthetho kaMosis. Futhi kuthiwa wena uthi makangabolùsi abantwana bawo, bangawalandeli namasiko esiJuda.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kunjalonje aza kuva ukuba ufikile. Uthi kungenziwa ntoni?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Phulaphula ke, sikucebise! Apha kukho amadoda amane azibophe ngesifungo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngoko ke wena zibandakanye nawo, ungene *ekuhlanjululweni, uze uwahlawulele iindleko zawo, abe nako ukuzicheba iintloko zawo. Ngale ndlela ke wonke umntu uya kuqonda ukuba bubuxoki yonke le nto bayivileyo ngawe – ndaweni yaloo nto wena ngokwakho usawugcinile umthetho kaMosis.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kodwa zona iintlanga ezingamakholwa sasizibhalele ileta ngokwesigqibo sethu, sibayala ukuba bangakutyi ukutya kwedini, nanyama inegazi, nasilwanyana sikrwitshiweyo, futhi bazikhwebule ekurheletyeni.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ke kaloku uPawulos wahlangana nawo loo madoda, waza ngengomso walenza kunye nawo isiko lokuhlanjululwa. Waza ke waya endlwini kaThixo ukuya kwenza amalungiselelo alo mcimbi, ngokukodwa malunga nomnikelo owawuya kufuneka ekupheleni kwexesha lentlambululo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Xa zaziza kuphela iintsuku ezisixhenxe *zentlambululo, amaJuda athile ephondo laseAsiya ambona uPawulos *esendlwini kaThixo. Avusa uqhushululu ebantwini, ambamba uPawulos,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> akhwaza esithi: “MaSirayeli, yizani! Nantsi le ndoda ihamba ithetha kakubi ngamaSirayeli, *ngomthetho kaMosis, nangendlu kaThixo, kumntu wonke. Ngoku ize kungcolisa le ndawo ingcwele ngokungenisa iintlanga kuyo.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Babesitsho kuba babekhe bambona kaloku uTrofimo wase-Efese edolophini apho, ekunye noPawulos; ngoku ke babeba uPawulos umzise endlwini kaThixo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Yaba ludushe ke kuyo yonke idolophu; basuka indulumbane bonke abantu, bambamba uPawulos, bamqweqwedisela ngaphandle kwendlu kaThixo. Kwangoko bazivala iingcango.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Babeza kumbulala uPawulos ukuba kwakungafikanga lizwi kwingqwayi-ngqwayi yomkhosi wamaRoma, liyixelela ngodushe oluseJerusalem.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kwangoko ingqwayi-ngqwayi yesuka kunye namagosa ayo, neqela lamajoni, yasukela apho kolo dushe. Bakuyibona isiza namajoni, bayeka ukumbetha uPawulos abantu.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ingqwayi-ngqwayi yaya kuPawulos, yambamba, yayalela nokuba akhonkxwe ngamatyathanga amabini. Yaza ke yabuza isithi: “Ngubani lo mntu? Wenze ntoni?”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Loo ndimbane yaphendula, abanye bethetha le, abanye bethetha leya. Kwakuphithizela kangangokuba ingqwayi-ngqwayi ayizange ikuqonde ncam okwakwenzekile, yaza ke yayalela ukuba uPawulos asiwe enqabeni yamajoni.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Baya kufika naye ezitepsini, kwanyanzeleka ukuba amthwale apho amajoni, ngenxa yesiphithi-phithi sabantu.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bonke babemlandela bekhwaza besithi: “Bulala!”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Xa babeza kungena enqabeni, wathi uPawulos kwingqwayi-ngqwayi yomkhosi: “Ndingákhe ndithethe nawe?” Ingqwayi-ngqwayi ithe: “Kanti uyasazi isiGrike?",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kuthe kanti akunguye laa mJiputa wakha wadala uqhushululu apha, wakhokelela endle amawaka amane abarhubuluzi bexhobile?”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Uphendule wathi uPawulos: “Mna ndingumJuda; ndazalelwa eTarso kwelaseKiliki. Ndingummi wedolophu ebalulekileyo. Ndivumele ndikhe ndibhekise ilizwi kwaba bantu.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Yamvumela ingqwayi-ngqwayi, waza ke uPawulos emi ezitepsini wawangawangisa ngesandla ukuba bathi cwaka abantu, wadanduluka ngesiHebhere esithi:"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Mawethu, nani bobawo, khanindiphulaphule xa ndiziphendulelayo.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bathi bakumva ukuba uthetha ngesiHebhere, bathi cwaka. Waza waqhuba wathi uPawulos:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Mna ndingumJuda, ndazalelwa eTarso kwelaseKiliki, kodwa ndakhulela apha eJerusalem, ndingumfundi kaGamaliyeli. Ndafumana ingqeqesho ecokisekileyo kumthetho wookhokho bethu; futhi ndandizinikele kuThixo, ndinjengokuba ninjalo nani namhlanje.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ndandibatshutshis' ukufa abantu abalandela le Ndlela. Ndandiwabamba amadoda kwanabafazi, ndibafake entolongweni.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Umbingeleli omkhulu *neBhunga xa lilonke bangangqina ukuba ndithetha inyaniso xa nditshoyo. Ndandithatha iincwadi kubo, zibhalelwe amaJuda aseDamasko, ndize mna ndihambe ndiye kubamba abantu, ndibabuyise bekhonkxiwe, ndibazise eJerusalem, ukuze bohlwaywe.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Ndathi xa ndandihamba ndisondela eDamasko, emini emaqanda, ndabona ukukhanya okuqaqambileyo esibhakabhakeni kundibengezelela ngeenxa zonke.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ndawa emhlabeni, ndaza ndeva ilizwi lisithi: ‘Sawule, Sawule, unditshutshisela ntoni na?’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ndabuza ndathi: ‘Ungubani wena, Nkosi?’ Laphendula lathi: ‘NdinguYesu waseNazarete, lo umtshutshisayo.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Amadoda endandihamba nawo akubona okunene ukukhanya, kodwa akazange ayive into ethethwa ngulowo wayethetha nam.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ndabuza ndathi: ‘Ndingenza ntoni, Nkosi?’ Yaza yathi iNkosi kum: ‘Vuka, uye eDamasko; woyixelelwa khona apho into yonke akumisele ukuba uyenze uThixo.’",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ukubengezela kokukhanya oko ndakubonayo kwanditsho ndayimfama, baza abo babendiphahlile bandibamba ngesandla, bandikhokelela eDamasko.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Apho ke kwakukho indoda ethile egama linguHananiya. Yayiyindoda ewuzondeleleyo iwuthobele *umthetho, ihlonelwa kakhulu ngawo onke amaJuda aseDamasko.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Yeza yafika yema ecaleni kwam, yathi: ‘Sawule, mfondini, buya ubone.’ Kanye ngaloo mzuzu avuleka amehlo am, ndaza ndabona.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Wathi: ‘UThixo wookhokho bethu ukukhethele ukuba ukwazi ukuthanda kwakhe, ukuze usibone isiCaka sakhe esililungisa, uve ilizwi lakhe lithetha nawe,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> kuba uya kuba lingqina lakhe, wazise bonke abantu izinto ozibonileyo nozivileyo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngoku ke usalindele ntoni? Vuka, ubhaptizwe, zixolelwe izono zakho ngokubiza igama lakhe.’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Ndaphindela kwaseJerusalem, apho ndathi *ndisendlwini kaThixo ndithandaza, ndaba nombono.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ndabona iNkosi isithi kum: ‘Khawuleza umke eJerusalem, kuba abantu balapha abayi kubamkela ubungqina bakho ngam.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ndathi ke mna: ‘Nkosi, bazi kakuhle ukuba ndandifika ndibabambe abo bazinikele kuwe, ndibabethele apho *ezindlwini zesikhungo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kanti nangamhla kwakubulawa uStefano, ingqina lakho, nam ndandikho. Ndandihambisana nokugwintwa kwakhe, neempahla zababemgebenga zigcinwe ndim lo.’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Yathi kum iNkosi: ‘Hamba, kuba ndiza kukuthuma kude kweleentlanga.’ ”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Babemphulaphule abantu uPawulos, kwada kwaza kutsho kule ndawo; basuka ke batsho ngentswahla besithi: “Msuse! Bulala loo nto!”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kwakuthe nzwii yingxolo, bejiwuzisa iimpahla zabo, kuqhuma uthuli.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ingqwayi-ngqwayi yomkhosi wamajoni amaRoma yathi uPawulos makangeniswe enqabeni yawo, akatswe, kuncinwe unobangela wento amxhibe ngayo amaJuda, ukuze angxole kangaka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kuthe sebembophelele, beza kumkatsa, uPawulos wabhekisa kumphathi-butho owayemi apho, wathi: “Khawutsho, kusemthethweni ukuba ungámbetha ummi ongumRoma engakhanga afunyanwe enetyala?”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Umphathi-butho akuyiva le nto, waya kwingqwayi-ngqwayi, wathi: “Uza kuthini ke? Lo mfo ngummi ongumRoma.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ingqwayi-ngqwayi ke yaya kuPawulos, yathi: “Khawutsho: ungummi ongumRoma wena?” Wavuma uPawulos.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ingqwayi-ngqwayi yaqhuba isithi: “Ndahlawula imali eninzi ukuze ndibe ngummi ongumRoma.” UPawulos wathi ukuphendula: “Kodwa ke mna ndinguye ngokuzalwa.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kwangoko loo madoda ayeza kumncina uPawulos arhoxa, ingqwayi-ngqwayi yoyika yakuqonda ukuba uPawulos wayengummi ongumRoma, imkhonkxe ngamatyathanga nje.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ingqwayi-ngqwayi yafuna ukuqiniseka ngetyala awayemmangalela ngalo amaJuda uPawulos. Ithe ke ngengomso makakhululwe amatyathanga uPawulos, kubizwe ababingeleli abaziintloko kunye *neBhunga xa lilonke. Yaza ke yeza kummisa phambi kwentlanganiso uPawulos."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> UPawulos wawajonga ntsho amalungu eBhunga, wathi: “Mawethu, kude kuze kuba yile mininje andinasazela nganto ngobomi bam bonke phambi koThixo.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Akutsho, umbingeleli omkhulu uHananiya wayalela ukuba uPawulos ampakazwe emlonyeni ngabo babekufuphi naye.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Waphendula uPawulos wathi: “UThixo uya kukubetha, ludongandini luvetiweyo; uchophele ukundigweba ngokomthetho, kodwa kwawena uyawaphula umthetho, uthi mandibethwe!”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Amadoda awayekufuphi noPawulos athi kuye: “Ngumbingeleli omkhulu kaThixo lo umthukayo!”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> UPawulos wathi: “Hayi, mawethu, bendingamazi ukuba ungumbingeleli omkhulu. Kaloku *iziBhalo zithi: ‘Ungàthethi kakubi ngomlawuli wabantu bakho.’”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Akuqonda uPawulos ukuba kweli qela kukho *abaSadusi kwakunye *nabaFarasi, wabhekisa eBhungeni apho, wathi: “Mawethu, mna ndingumFarasi ongunyana womFarasi. Ndisematyaleni nje kungenxa yokuba ndinethemba lokuba abafileyo baya kuvuka.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Akutsho abaFarasi nabaSadusi baxabana bodwa, baza bahlukana kubini.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kaloku bona abaSadusi bathi abantu abayi kuvuka ekufeni, bakwathi akukho zithunywa zezulu, akukho namimoya, kodwa abaFarasi bona bayakholelewa kwezi zinto zontathu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kwathi ke kwakuba njalo, kwaxokozela, abanye babachazi-mthetho beqela labaFarasi baphakama bekhalaza besithi: “Thina asifumani nto ingalunganga kule ndoda! Mhlawumbi ngenene umoya othile okanye isithunywa sezulu sithethile nayo.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ingxoxo leyo yakhula kangangokuba ingqwayi-ngqwayi yaba sexhaleni lokuba uPawulos bosuka bamthi qwenge-qwenge. Ngoko ke yayalela ukuba amajoni amthathe uPawulos apho entlanganisweni, aye naye enqabeni yomkhosi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngobo busuku iNkosi yema ngakuPawulos, yathi: “Qina! Njengokuba undingqine apha eJerusalem nje, kufuneka wenze kwaloo nto naseRoma.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngentsasa elandelayo amaJuda adibana enza iyelenqe. Azibopha ngesifungo sokuba angatyi angaseli engambulalanga uPawulos.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ayengaphezu kwamashumi amane kweli yelenqe.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Aza ke aya kubabingeleli abaziintloko nakubadala athi: “Sizibophe ngesifungo, saye sizimisele ukuba singafaki nto phantsi kwempumlo singekambulali uPawulos.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nina ke *neBhunga thumelani kumphathi-mkhosi wamaRoma ukuba azise uPawulos kuni, nenze ngathi nisafuna ukuncina inyaniso ngaye. Thina ke soba sesilungile, simhlasele simbulale engekafiki kuni.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kodwa weva ngeli yelenqe unyana wodade boPawulos, waza ke waya kungena enqabeni yamajoni, wamxelela ngalo uPawulos.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> UPawulos ubize umphathi-butho, wathi kuye: “Yisa lo mfana kwingqwayi-ngqwayi. Kukho into afuna ukuyixelela yona.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Umphathi-butho wamthatha wamsa kwingqwayi-ngqwayi, wafika wathi: “Ndibizwe ngumbanjwa uPawulos, wathi mandize nalo mfana kuwe, kuba kukho into aza kukuxelela yona.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ingqwayi-ngqwayi imbambe ngesandla umfana lowo, yamtsalela bucala, yambuza isithi: “Uze kundixelela ntoni?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Uthe umfana: “Iziphathamandla zamaJuda zivumelene ukuba zikucele ngomso, ukhe uthumele uPawulos eBhungeni, zisenza ngathi kukho indawo ebalulekileyo elifuna ukuyiqonda kuye iBhunga.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kodwa uze ungavumi ukuyiva loo nto, ngoba kukho amadoda angaphezu kwamashumi amane alalele uPawulos endleleni. Afungile ukuba akayi kutya, engayi kusela, ade ambulale. Nangoku selelungile, elindele ukuba uvume.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ithe ingqwayi-ngqwayi: “Uzungayithethi mntwini into yokuba undixelele ngeli yelenqe.” Yaza yamndulula umfana lowo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ingqwayi-ngqwayi ithe yabiza abaphathi-mabutho bayo ababini, yathi kubo: “Lungiselelani ukuya eKhesariya ngokuhlwanje ngentsimbi yethoba. Ze nihambe namakhulu amabini amajoni kunye namashumi asixhenxe amajoni akhwele amahashe, kwakunye namakhulu amabini amajoni aphatha iintshuntshe.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Nithathe namahashe okukhwela, uPawulos nimse kuFelekis irhuluneli engenzakalanga.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ingqwayi-ngqwayi yabhala ileta, yenjenje:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “UKlawudiyo Lisiya ubulisa ohloniphekileyo uFelekis irhuluneli.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Le ndoda âyibamba amaJuda eza kuyibulala. Ndivile ukuba ingummi ongumRoma, ndaya kuyihlangula ngamajoni.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ndithe ke ngokufuna ukuqonda isityholo abayibeka sona, ndayisa *eBhungeni lawo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Apho ke kuye kwacaca ukuba ayenzanga tyala lokuba ingagwetyelwa ukufa, nokuba mayivalelwe entolongweni. Isityholo ebekwa sona siphathelele kwimpikiswano ngomthetho wabo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ndithe ke ndakuva ukuba kukho amaJuda azungula ukuyibulala, ndagqiba ukuba ndiyithumele kuwe. Abamangali nabo ndibaxelele ukuba beze kuyimangalela kuwe.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Amajoni enza njengoko ayeyalelwe. Amthatha uPawulos kwangobo busuku, aya kufika naye eAntipatri.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ngengomso ahamba ngeenyawo abuyela eJerusalem, aza awamahashe ahamba naye.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Aya kufika naye eKhesariya, ayinika irhuluneli ileta leyo, amnikezela kuyo noPawulos.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Iyifundile ileta irhuluneli, yambuza uPawulos ukuba wayengowaliphi na iphondo. Yakuva ukuba wayengowaseKiliki",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> yathi: “Ityala lakho liya kuthethwa kwakufika abamangali.” Yathi uPawulos makagcinwe ebhotwe likaHerode."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Emva kweentsuku ezintlanu umbingeleli omkhulu uHananiya waya eKhesariya, ekunye nabadala abathile noTertulo igqwetha. Bavela phambi kwerhuluneli bemmangalela uPawulos.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Weziswa uPawulos, waza uTertulo wammangalela wenjenje: “Felekis, mhlekazi ohloniphekileyo, ukulawula kwakho ngobulumko kuze nethuba elide loxolo. Nezinye izinto eziyimfuneko zenkqubela siyazibona zisenzeka kweli lizwe lethu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngamaxesha onke siyazamkela ezi zinto, futhi sinongazenzisiyo umbulelo kuwe.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Andifuni ukulidla ixesha lakho, ngoko ke ndicela ukuba usiphulaphule ngobulali esi simangalo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Lo mfo simfumene engumdodobalisi oyingozi. Uhamba ephemba udushe phakathi kwamaJuda kulo lonke elimiweyo; futhi uyinkokheli yegqiza lamaNazarete.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Samfumana ezama ukunyelisa *indlu kaThixo, saza sambamba. [Sasifuna ukumgweba ngokomthetho wethu,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> kodwa kwafika umphathi-mkhosi uLisiya wamhlutha kakubi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ULisiya wayalela ukuba aze kumangalelwa kuwe.] Nawe ngokwakho ekumvavanyeni kwakho uya kuziqonda uziva ngaye ezi zinto simmangalela ngazo.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> NamaJuda asingqina esi simangalo ukuba siyinyaniso.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Irhuluneli yanqwala kuPawulos ukuba athethe, waza wathi: “Ndiyazi ukuba uneminyaka emininzi ugweba kwesi sizwe; yiyo loo nto ndivuyayo kuba ndiziphendulela phambi kwakho.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nawe unokuyiqonda into yokuba azingaphezu kweshumi elinambini iintsuku ndayayo eJerusalem ndiye kunqula.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> AmaJuda akandifumananga ndixoxa namntu *endlwini kaThixo, engandifumananga ndiphembelela dushe bantwini *ezindlwini zesikhungo, okanye naphi na apho edolophini.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Futhi akanabo ubungqina obuphathekayo malunga nezi zinto andityhola ngazo ngoku.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Le yona into ndiyayivuma: Ndikhonza uThixo wookhokho bethu ngokulandela iNdlela le athi wona ayikho mgaqweni. Ndikholwa zizo zonke izinto ezibhaliweyo encwadini *yomthetho kaMosis nasezincwadini *zabashumayeli.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ndibambelele ethembeni elinye nabo abamangali, eli lokuba bonke abantu, abalungileyo nabangalunganga, baya kuvuka ekufeni.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ndibe ke ndizama kangangoko ndinako ukuba ndihlale ndingenasazela nganto phambi koThixo naphambi kwabantu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Ndakha ndangabikho iminyaka emininzi eJerusalem, ndaza emva koko ndaya khona ndisisela abantu bakowethu imali, futhi ndisiya kwenza amadini.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ndandisendlwini kaThixo apho ke, ukundifikela kwawo amaJuda ekubeni sendigqibe ukwenza *intlambululo. Ndandingekho esiphithi-phithini, futhi kungekho naqhushululu olo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ayekhona amaJuda athile ephondo laseAsiya; ebefanele ukuba alapha phambi kwakho andimangalele ngokwawo, xa enendawo ngakum.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Okanye khawutsho kula madoda axele ukuba andifumana ndinatyala lini na ngokuya ndandimi phambi kweBhunga.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Into inye endakhala ngayo naphambi kwawo, ndathi: ‘Ndigwetywa nje namhlanje, kungenxa yokukholelwa ukuba abafileyo baya kuvuka.’ ”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Waza ke uFelekis owayeyazi kakuhle iNdlela le, walimisa ityala, wathi: “Ndiya kuligweba ityala lakho akufika umphathi-mkhosi uLisiya.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Wayalela umphathi-butho owayegada uPawulos ukuba amgcine, kodwa angabi ngqongqo, azivumele izihlobo zakhe zimlungiselele.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kwakudlula iintsuku uFelekis wafika noDrusila umkakhe, umJudakazi. Wambiza uPawulos, waza wamphulaphula ethetha ngokholo kuKrestu Yesu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kodwa wahambisa uPawulos echaza ngokuziphatha kakuhle, ukuzeyisa, nangomhla womgwebo, uFelekis watsho woyika wathi: “Ungakhe umke ngoku; ndiya kuphinda ndikubize xa ndinethuba.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Wayenethemba lokuba mhlawumbi angahle anyotywe nguPawulos; kungesi sizathu ke wayesoloko emana ukumbiza ancokole naye.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Emva kweminyaka emibini uPorkiyo Festo waba yirhuluneli endaweni kaFelekis. Ngenxa yokuba uFelekis wayefuna ukuzenza mhle kumaJuda, wamshiya entolongweni apho uPawulos."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Akuba ntsuku-ntathu efikile kwelo phondo uFesto, wesuka eKhesariya, wahambela eJerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ababingeleli abaziintloko nabakhokeli bamaJuda, bezisa izityholo kuye ngoPawulos. Bamcenga uFesto",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ukuba ancede amse eJerusalem uPawulos, kuba babefuna ukumlalela endleleni, bamgwinte.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wathi uFesto kubo: “UPawulos uselugcinweni entolongweni eKhesariya. Ndibe nam ngokwam ndiza kuya khona kwakamsinyane.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Iinkokheli zenu ze zihambe nam ukuya eKhesariya, ziye kummangalela khona, ukuba ngaba kukho ityala alenzileyo.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Akuba echithe malunga nesibhozo ukuya eshumini leentsuku phakathi kwabo uFesto, wabuyela eKhesariya. Ngengomso xa wayechophele amatyala, uthe makabizwe uPawulos.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Akufika ke uPawulos, amaJuda awayevela eJerusalem athi emngqongile ambeka izityholo ezinzima, kodwa zazingenabunyaniso xa zizonke.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UPawulos yena waziphendulela wathi: “Akukho nanye into endiyenzileyo echasene nomthetho wamaJuda, okanye *indlu kaThixo, okanye *uKhesare.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ezama ukuzenza mhle kumaJuda, uFesto wathi kuPawulos: “Ungathanda ukuya eJerusalem ukuze ndilichophele khona ityala lakho ngezi zityholo?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Waphendula uPawulos wathi: “Apha ndimi enkundleni kaKhesare, kanye apho limelwe kukuthethwa khona ityala lam. Akukho nto ndiwone ngayo amaJuda, njengoko nawe ngokwakho uqonda.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ke ukuba umthetho ndiwaphule ndona kangangokuba ndimelwe kukugwetyelwa ukufa, andinqweneli kuyibaleka nayo loo ndawo. Kodwa ke ukuba azinabunyaniso izityholo endibekwa zona, akukho bani unokundinikezela kumaJuda. Ndibhenela kuKhesare.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> UFesto ukhe wadlana indlebe namaphakathi akhe, wandul' ukuthi kuPawulos: “Ubhenela kuKhesare; kulungile ke, uza kuya kuKhesare.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ekuhambeni kwexesha ukumkani uAgripa nowakwakhe uBhernike baya eKhesariya, beye kuvuyisana noFesto ngokufika kwakhe.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Emva kweentsuku bekhona uFesto wachazela ukumkani ngemeko kaPawulos, esithi: “Apha kukho indoda eyashiywa ingumbanjwa nguFelekis.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ndithe xa bendiseJerusalem, ababingeleli abaziintloko bamaJuda nabadala bazisa kum izityholo ngale ndoda ukuba ndiyigwebe.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kodwa ndabaxelela ukuba inkqubo yamaRoma ayivumi ukuba umntu agwetywe engakhange ajongane nabamangaleli bakhe aziphendulele.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bathe ke bakuza apha andachitha xesha, ndathi ngengomso ndalichophela ityala elo, ndathi mayibizwe le ndoda.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Abamangali bavela bamtyhola, kodwa kungengazo iindawo ezimbi endandiba bomtyhola ngazo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kuphela nje yaba yimpikiswano ngonqulo lwabo, nangendoda ethile eyafayo, egama linguYesu, athi yena uPawulos ihleli.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ndithe ngenxa yokungabi nabungqina buphathekayo ngeli tyala, ndaqonda kuPawulos ukuba akangethandi na ukuba eli tyala liye kuthethwa eJerusalem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kodwa ke uPawulos usuke wabhenela *kuKhesare. Ubone ukuba makahlale engumbanjwa lide ityala lakhe libe nokuviwa nguMhlekazi ngokwakhe. Ke ndathi makagcinwe de ndimthumele kuKhesare.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Wathi uAgripa: “Nam ndingathanda ukukhe ndiyive le ndoda.” “Uza kuyiva ngomso oku,” utshilo uFesto.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ngengomso uAgripa noBhernike bangena bewongekile apho enkundleni, benabaphathi-mkhosi namadoda aphambili apho edolophini. UFesto wathi makubizwe uPawulos, waza ke wangeniswa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> UFesto wathetha wathi: “Kumkani Agripa, nani nonke nina nikhoyo apha, le ndoda niyibona apha ikhalazelwa ngawo onke amaJuda, apha naseJerusalem. Athi ayisafanelanga kudla bomi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kodwa mna andifumananga nto ingáyenza igwetyelwe ukufa. Nangenxa yokuba yona ngokwayo ibhenele kuKhesare, nam ke ndigqiba ukuba ndiyithumele kuye.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kodwa andikabi nayo inkcazelo ezeleyo endingayenzela uKhesare ngayo. Kungoko ke ndiyizise apha phambi kwenu, ngakumbi wena, kumkani Agripa, ukuze sithi emva kokulivavanya eli tyala layo, ndikwazi ukubhala ngalo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kuba kum ayiqondakali into yokuba ndithumele umbanjwa zingacacanga izityholo abekwa zona.”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> UAgripa wathi kuPawulos: “Uvumelekile ukuzithethelela.” UPawulos ke waphakamisa isandla, wenjenje ukuziphendulela:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Kumkani Agripa, ndinenyhweba ukuba ndibe ndiza kuziphendulela phambi kwakho namhlanje, kuzo zonke ezi ndawo ndityholwa ngazo ngamaJuda;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> nangakumbi kuba wena unolwazi ngamasiko amaJuda nezinye iinkcukacha zobuJuda. Uze undiphulaphule ngenyameko ke.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Iyaziwa ngawo onke amaJuda indlela endandiziphethe ngayo kwandiselula. Ayayazi kwakudala indlela endandihlala ngayo kummandla wakowethu naseJerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kudala kakade esazi, ukuba angathanda ukuyingqina loo nto, ukuba mna kwasekuqaleni ndaba lilungu lelona qela lingqongqo kunqulo lwakowethu, iqela *labaFarasi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kungokunje naku ndimi apha, ndize ematyaleni ngenxa yethemba endinalo kwidinga uThixo âlenza nookhokho bethu;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> kanye elo dinga zililangazelelayo xa zizonke ezi zizwe zakowethu zilishumi elinambini, njengoko zimnqula uThixo imini nobusuku. Kungenxa yeli themba ke, mhlekazi, endimangalela nje amaJuda.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kungani na ningakholwa nje, maJuda, ukuba uThixo uyabavusa abafileyo?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Mna lo ndandiba yinto efanelekileyo ukwenza nayiphi na into, ndilichasa igama likaYesu waseNazarete.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ndandisenza loo nto kanye eJerusalem. Ndandigunyaziswa ngababingeleli abaziintloko ukuba ndivalele entolongweni abantu bakaThixo abaninzi. Kwakusithi xa begwetyelwa ukufa, nam ndihambisane neso sigqibo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Amaxesha ngamaxesha ndandisiya *ezindlwini zesikhungo, ndifike ndibohlwaye, ndisenzela ukuba bahlukane nokholo lwabo. Ngangengcwangu endandinayo ngakubo ndandide ndiye kubatshutshisa nakwezikude iidolophu.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Kwakungale njongo ke kanye ukuze ndiye eDamasko, ndinamagunya endawafumana kubabingeleli abaziintloko.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Endleleni apho, emini emaqanda, mhlekazi, ndabona ukukhanya okubengezela ngaphezu kokukhanya kwelanga, kuvela esibhakabhakeni, kundibengezelela ngeenxa zonke, naloo madoda ndandihamba nawo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Xa sisonke sawa phantsi, ndaza ndeva ilizwi lithetha nam ngesiHebhere, lisithi: ‘Sawule, Sawule, unditshutshisela ntoni? Uyazenzakalisa ngezi nkani zakho!’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ‘Ungubani, Nkosi?’ ndabuza ndatsho. Yathi iNkosi: ‘Mna ndinguYesu, lo umtshutshisayo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Vuka ume ngeenyawo. Ndibonakala kuwe ngesi sizathu sokuba ndikumisele ube sisicaka sam, ungqine kwabanye abantu ngokundibona kwakho namhlanje, nangezinto endisaza kukubonisa zona.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ndikuhlangula kumaSirayeli nasezintlangeni; phofu ndikuthuma kwakuzo,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ukuba uvule amehlo azo, uziguqule ziphume ebumnyameni, zize ekukhanyeni, ziphume egunyeni likaSathana, zize kuThixo, ukuze zithi ngenxa yokuzinikela kum zixolelwe izono zazo, futhi zizuze indawo phakathi kwabantu bakaThixo abanyuliweyo.’ ”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Ngoko ke, kumkani Agripa, ndawuthobela umbono lowo wawuvela ezulwini.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ndaqala eDamasko ndaya eJerusalem, nakuwo wonke umhlaba wakwaJuda, nakweleentlanga, ndashumayela ukuba baguquke, beze kuThixo, benze izinto ezibonakalisayo ukuba baguqukile.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Sesi sizathu ke esabangela ukuba amaJuda andihlasele endlwini kaThixo, efuna ukundibulala.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kodwa kude kwayile mini uThixo endinceda; nangoku ndimi apha ndingqina kubo bonke, abaphakamileyo nabaphantsi ngokufanayo. Le nto ndiyithethayo ikwayiloo nto bayithethayo *abashumayeli bamandulo kwakunye noMosis,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> le yokuba uKrestu umelwe kukuva ubunzima, aze abe ngowokuqala ukuvuka kwabafileyo, avakalise ukuvela komsobomvu wosindiso kumaJuda nasezintlangeni.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Wathi uPawulos esazithethelela njalo, uFesto wakhwaza wathi: “Uphambene, Pawulos! Imfundo eninzi iyakuphambanisa!”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> UPawulos waphendula wathi: “Andiphambananga, mhlekazi Festo; la mazwi ndiwathethayo ayinyaniso, futhi ngawengqondo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Mhlekazi Agripa, ndingathetha phandle nawe, kuba wena uyazazi ezi zinto. Ndiqinisekile ukuba waziqaphela xa zizonke, kuba le nto ayizange ifihlakale ukwenzeka kwayo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kumkani Agripa, uyakholwa ludaba *lwabashumayeli bamandulo? Kambe ndiyazi ukuba uyakholwa!”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Wathi uAgripa kuPawulos: “Kwangoku sowufuna ukundenza umKrestu nam?”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> UPawulos waphendula wathi: “Nokuba kukwangoku, nokuba kukade, ngumthandazo wam ukuba ingabi nguwe wedwa, kodwa ibe ngabo bonke abandiphulaphuleyo namhlanje, babe njengam; kodwa ke noko bona bangakhonkxwa.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Waza ke ukumkani, irhuluneli, noBhernike, nabo bonke ababelapho, baphakama,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> baza xa bemkayo wathi omnye komnye: “Le ndoda ayenzanga nto engade ibulawe okanye ifakwe entolongweni ngenxa yayo.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Wathi uAgripa kuFesto: “Le ndoda ngeyikhululwa ukuba ibingabhenelanga *kuKhesare.”"
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kwakuba kugqityiwe ukuba sisiwe ngenqanawa eItali, uPawulos ekunye namanye amabanjwa banikelwa kuJuliyo, owayengumphathi-butho lomkhosi ekuthiwa libutho *likaKhesare.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Sangena enqanaweni eyayivela eAdramita, iza kunduluka iye kwizikhululo-nqanawe zephondo laseAsiya, sahamba ngayo. Wayekunye nathi uAristarko waseTesalonika, ekummandla waseMakedoni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sagaleleka eSidon ngemini elandelayo. UJuliyo wamphatha ngobubele uPawulos, wamvumela ukuba aye kubona abalingane bakhe, khon' ukuze bamtende.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sanduluka apho, sathi kuba umoya wawusityhala uvela ngaphambili, sahamba ngecala langasempuma yeSipro, elalingenamoya.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sacanda kulwandle olungaseKiliki nasePamfili, saya kungena eMira kummandla waseLikiya.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Apho umphathi-butho wafumana inqanawa eyayiza kuya eItali, ivela eAlesandriya, sangena kuyo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sahamba iintsuku icotha inqanawa, sada emva kokuhamba nzima kakhulu, saya kufika ngakwidolophu iKinido. Umoya awusivumelanga ukuba sihambe ngqo ngaloo ndlela, saza ke sehla ngecala elingenamoya elikumzantsi weKrete, saya kudlula ngaseSalimone.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Salugudla unxweme, sihamba nzima, saya kungena kwindawo ekuthiwa ngamaChweba aMahle, eyayingekude kwidolophu iLaseya.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sahlala ixesha elide apho, kwada kwacaca ukuba koba yingozi ukuqhubela phambili ihambo yethu, kuba kwakusekudlule nomhla wamaJuda wozilo ekwindla. Ke ngoko uPawulos wenza esi silumkiso:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Madoda, ndibona ukuba luza kuba nengozi uhambo lwethu ukusuka apha. Umthwalo uza konakala kakhulu, nenqanawa yaphuke, kufe nabantu.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kodwa umphathi-butho zange ayihoye le ntetho kaPawulos, wasuka weva into ethethwa ngumphathi woomatiloshe, nomnini-nqanawa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Isikhululo-nqanawa eso sasingàkulungele ukuba kungáchithwa ubusika kuso, lwaye uninzi lwamadoda lufuna ukuba kungenwe elwandle, kulingwe ukuya kufika eFenike, ukuba kwakunokwenzeka. Esi sikhululo-nqanawa saseKrete, siziwa ngumoya wasemzantsi-ntshona kunye novela emntla-ntshona, kwakunokuhlalwa kuso ebusika.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kwavela umoyana ngasezantsi, aza amadoda acinga ukuba angalilinga iqhinga lawo. Bayitsalela enqanaweni iankile, baza ke bayiqhuba inqanawa begudle unxweme lwaseKrete.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kodwa kwakamsinyane kwabakho umoyakazi ekuthiwa nguMntla-mpuma, uvela ngasesiqithini apho.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Wayintlitha inqanawa; kwathi kuba yayingenakuqhutywa ijonge ngqo emoyeni inqanawa, asabi salinga, sasuka sayiyeka yadudulwa ngumoya.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Safumana indawo esithileyo ukudlula kwethu emazantsi esiqithana iKhawuda. Salitsalela enqanaweni apho iphenyana kunzima.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Oomatiloshe balibophelela, baza bayiqamangela ngentsontela inqanawa. Babesoyika ukuba bangaxinga enyeleni yonxweme xa bedlula ngaseLibhiya. Bayithoba ke iseyile ukuze inqanawa ityhalwe ngumoya.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Lwavuthuza njalo uqhwithela, baza ngengomso baqala bawulahlela elwandle umthwalo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kwathi ngolwesithathu usuku bazilahla ngezandla zabo iimpahla zenqanawa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Yaba ziintsuku ezininzi singenakulibona ilanga neenkwenkwezi, yaye uqhwithela lona lusitsho ukuvuthuza. Ekugqibeleni sancama ukuba singásinda.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Emva kwexesha elide amadoda lawo engatyi, waphakama uPawulos wathi: “Madoda, ukuba nanindivile asemka eKrete, ngesiwuphephile wonke lo monakalo nale lahleko ingaka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kodwa ke qinani, ndiyanibongoza! Kuba akukho bani uza kuphulukana nobomi bakhe; yinqanawa yodwa eza konakala.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kuba phezolo isithunywa sikaThixo, lo ndingowakhe ndimnqulayo, sifike kum,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> sathi: ‘Sukoyika, Pawulos! Uza kuma phambi *koKhesare. UThixo ngokulunga kwakhe uza kubasindisa bonke aba uhamba nabo.’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ngoko ke, madoda, qinani; kuba ndimthembile uThixo ukuba uya kwenza njengoko andixeleleyo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kodwa ke siya kududulwa siye kuphoswa kunxweme lwesiqithi esithile.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Yayibubusuku beshumi elinesine sidudulwa luqhwithela kuLwandle lweAdriya. Kwathi malunga phakathi kobusuku, oomatiloshe bakrokrela ukuba asikude emhlabeni.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Baphosa intambo ebotshelelwe intsimbi emanzini, belinganisa ubunzulu bamanzi, baza bafumana ingamashumi amathathu anantandathu eemitha ubunzulu. Baphinda emva koko, baza bafumana amashumi amabini anesixhenxe eemitha.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bathi ngenxa yokuba besoyika ukuba isuke inqanawa yethu iphoseke ematyeni, bazithoba zane iiankile esinqeni senqanawa, sebelangazelela ukuba kuse.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Oomatiloshe bazama ukuzímela, bathobela iphenyane emanzini, bezenza ngathi ba-ankila umphambili wenqanawa.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kodwa wathi uPawulos kumphathi-butho: “Ukuba oomatiloshe abahlali apha enqanaweni, aninakusinda.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Asuka ke amajoni azinqumla iintsontela ezazibambe iphenyane, laza lona lawa emanzini.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ekuseni uPawulos wabacenga ukuba batye, esithi: “Ngoku lishumi elinesine leentsuku nilindile, ningasafaki nento le etyiwayo emlonyeni.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ndiyanibongoza, yityani. Niya kuncedwa kukutya kule ngozi. Anisayi kulahlekelwa nalunwele olu.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Akuba etshilo uPawulos, wathatha isonka, wabulela kuThixo, watya phambi kwabo.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bomelezeka ke, baza bathatha ukutya, batya bonke.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Sasingamakhulu amabini anamashumi asixhenxe anesithandathu sisonke.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bakuba betyile, bawuphungula umthwalo wenqanawa ngokuphosa ingqolowa elwandle.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Kwakuba kusile oomatiloshe babona unxweme abangalunakananga kakuhle, kodwa baqaphela indawo enentlabathi, baza bazimisela ukuya kuyimisa khona inqanawa xa benako.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ngoko ke bazinqumla iiankile, zasala elwandle, kwangelo xesha linye bazikhulula neentsontela ezazibambe amaphini okugwedla. Bayiphakamisa iseyile ekumphambili wenqanawa, ukuze umoya uyiqhubele phambili elunxwemeni inqanawa.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Kodwa inqanawa yasuka yabaleka yaya kungena endulini yesanti ephantsi kwamanzi; umphambili wenqanawa wagxumekeka apho waxinga awashukuma, isinqe senqanawa sona santlithwa saziingceba ngamaza alwayo.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Amajoni wona aceba ukuwabulala amabanjwa, ukuze angadadi azimele.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Kodwa umphathi wawo, efuna ukusindisa uPawulos, wawanqanda. Endaweni yaloo nto wathi amadoda akwaziyo ukudada makangene emanzini, adadele elunxwemeni;",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> baze abaseleyo balandele, bedada ngamaplanga, nangezinye izinto ababenokuzifumana. Xa sisonke ke sasinda ngaloo ndlela, saya kufika elunxwemeni singenawo nomkrwelo."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ekubeni sisindile safika apho esiqithini, safumana ukuba igama laso yiMalta.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Abantu balapho basenzela ububele. Yana imvula, kwaza kwabanda kakhulu. Ke kaloku abantu balapho basibasela umlilo, bebonisa ukusamkela kwabo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> UPawulos waqokelela ibathwana leenkuni, kwathi xa abasayo kwaphuma inyoka apho emlilweni, isiva ubushushu, yaza yamluma esandleni.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Abantu balapho bathi bakuyibona inyoka ijinga esandleni sikaPawulos bathi omnye komnye: “Lo mntu kucaca ukuba usisigebenga; nakuba esindile nje elwandle, akanakusinda kwimpindezelo kaThixo.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Wasuka yena uPawulos wayivuthulula yawa emlilweni apho inyoka leyo, yena akenzakala konke.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bona babelindele ukuba adumbe, okanye asuke afe. Kodwa emva kokulinda ithuba elide bengaboni nto ingaqhelekanga kuye, baziguqula iingcinga zabo, bathi unguthixo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mganyana nje ukusuka apho kwakukho amasimi kaPubliyo inkosi yeso siqithi. Wasamkela ngobubele, saza saziindwendwe zakhe iintsuku ezintathu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Uyise kaPubliyo wayelele enomkhuhlane nesisu segazi. Waza uPawulos waya kuye, wamthandazela, wambeka izandla, waphila.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Akuba emphilisile, kwatsho kweziswa bonke abantu abagulayo beso siqithi, baphiliswa nabo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Basinika izipho ezininzi, baza xa sihambayo basiphathisa izinto ezaziyimfuneko eluhambeni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Emva kweenyanga ezintathu sanduluka apho ngenqanawa eyayichithe ubusika esiqithini apho, isuka eAlesandriya. Igama layo kwakusithiwa yiDiyoskuri.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Saya kufika edolophini yaseSirakuse, saza sahlala khona iintsuku ezintathu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ukusuka apho sahamba saya kufika edolophini yaseRegiyo. Ngengomso kwabhudla umoya wangasezantsi, saza emva kweentsuku ezimbini saya kufika kwidolophu yasePutoli.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Apho ke safumana amakholwa, aza asicela ukuba sichithe iveki apho kuwo. Emva koko ke saya kufika eRoma.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Amakholwa aseRoma eva ukuba siyeza, aza amanye asihlangabeza eApiyaforo, amanye ke adibana nathi eTritabherne. Akuwabona uPawulos, wambulela uThixo, waza wakhuthazeka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Sakufika eRoma, wavunyelwa ukuba azihlalele endlwini yakhe uPawulos, kubekho ijoni elimgadileyo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Emva kweentsuku ezintathu, uPawulos wawabizela entlanganisweni amaJuda aziintloko alapho. Akuba ehlanganisene, wathi: “Mawethu, nakuba ndingabonanga nganto nje abantu bakowethu, ndingawatyeshelanga namasiko ookhokho, ndabanjwa kambe eJerusalem, ndaza ndanikelwa kumaRoma.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Andincina, aza afuna ukundikhulula, akungafumani tyala ndingabulawa ngenxa yalo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kodwa amaJuda aluchasa olu luvo, ndaza ke ndanyanzeleka ukuba ndibhenele *kuKhesare, nangona ndandingenasimangalo ndingasenzayo ngakubantu bakowethu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Yiyo le nto ndinibizele ukukhe ndinibone, ndithethe nani. Eneneni ndibanjiwe nje, kungenxa yalowo ulithemba lamaSirayeli.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Athe ke ukumphendula amaJuda: “Asikhange sifumane zileta ngawe zivela kwaJuda; akukhange kubekho namaJuda eza neendaba ngawe; kungakhange kubekho nanto imbi ithethwe ngawe.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kodwa ke singathanda ukuziva izimvo zakho, kuba siyazi ukuba kuyo yonke indawo liyachaswa eli qela uhambisana nalo.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bavumelana ngosuku noPawulos, kwaza ngaloo mini bafika bebaninzi apho wayehlala khona uPawulos. Waqala kwakusasa kwada kwahlwa ecacisa, ebachazela ngokuthwasa kolawulo lukaThixo. Wazama ukuboyisela kuYesu ngokucaphula *kumthetho kaMosis nakwiincwadi *zabashumayeli bamandulo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Abanye babo boyisakala ngamazwi akhe, abanye àbakholwa noko.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bemka ke bephikisana bodwa, akuba uPawulos ethe kubo: “Wathetha kakuhle kambe uMoya oyiNgcwele ngomshumayeli uIsaya kooyihlo-mkhulu,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> xa wathi: “ ‘Yiya uthi kwaba bantu: Nàkuphulaphula niphulaphule, ningaqondi noko; nàkujonga nijonge, ningaboni nto.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kuba ingqiqo yaba bantu ibuthuntu, bazivingcile iindlebe zabo, bawavala namehlo abo. Kungenjalo bebeya kubona, beve ngeendlebe zabo, baqonde ngeengqondo zabo, baze babuyele kum, ndize ndibaphilise;’ utsho uThixo.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> UPawulos wenjenje ukuyiphetha intetho yakhe: “Ngoko ke yazini ukuba udaba lukaThixo olungosindiso lusiwa ezintlangeni. Ziya kuluva zona.” [",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Emva kokuba uPawulos etshilo, emka amaJuda, ehamba exambulisana odwa.]",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Yaba mibini iminyaka uPawulos ehlala endlwini ayiqeshileyo, ezamkela ngobubele zonke iindwendwe zakhe.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Wayeshumayela ngokuthwasa kolawulo lukaThixo, efundisa iindaba ezingeNkosi uYesu Krestu, ethetha ngesibindi, engathintelwa nto."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;